nl: 各エピソード列をエピソード番号,ISOフォーマットされた放送日期,ゲストホスト,ミュージカルゲストを演奏者と歌,パネル参加者,キャッシュコートセレブティ,その演奏者のエピソード数,およびコンパクトな権利参照文字列をリストする.
sql:
WITH parsed AS (
  SELECT
    `Episode Number`,
    `Air Date`,
    `Guest Host`,
    `Musical Guest (Song performed)` AS `MusicalFull`,
    `Who knows the most about the guest host? Panelists`,
    `Coat Of Cash Wearing Celebrity`,
    instr(`Musical Guest (Song performed)`, '(') AS pos_open,
    instr(`Musical Guest (Song performed)`, ')') AS pos_close,
    instr(`Air Date`, ' ') AS pos1,
    instr(substr(`Air Date`, instr(`Air Date`, ' ')+1), ' ') AS pos2_rel
  FROM `table_1_1590967_7`
)
SELECT
  `Episode Number`,
  `Air Date`,
  '`' || `Guest Host` || '`' AS `Guest Host`,
  '`' || TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, 1, pos_open - 1)) || '`' AS `Musical Performer`,
  '`' || TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, pos_open + 1, pos_close - pos_open - 1)) || '`' AS `Song Performed`,
  `Who knows the most about the guest host? Panelists`,
  `Coat Of Cash Wearing Celebrity`,
  printf(
    '%04d-%02d-%02d',
    CAST(TRIM(substr(`Air Date`, pos1 + pos2_rel + 1)) AS INTEGER),
    CASE TRIM(substr(`Air Date`, pos1 + 1, pos2_rel - 1))
      WHEN 'January' THEN 1 WHEN 'February' THEN 2 WHEN 'March' THEN 3 WHEN 'April' THEN 4
      WHEN 'May' THEN 5 WHEN 'June' THEN 6 WHEN 'July' THEN 7 WHEN 'August' THEN 8
      WHEN 'September' THEN 9 WHEN 'October' THEN 10 WHEN 'November' THEN 11 WHEN 'December' THEN 12
      ELSE 0 END,
    CAST(TRIM(substr(`Air Date`, 1, pos1 - 1)) AS INTEGER)
  ) AS `ISO Air Date`,
  COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, 1, pos_open - 1))) AS `Episodes by Musical Performer`,
  '`' || `Air Date` || '` - `' || TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, 1, pos_open - 1)) || '` performing `' || TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, pos_open + 1, pos_close - pos_open - 1)) || '`' AS `Music Rights Reference`
FROM parsed
ORDER BY `ISO Air Date`;
db_sql:
WITH parsed AS (
  SELECT
    col0,
    col1,
    col2,
    col3 AS `MusicalFull`,
    col4,
    col5,
    instr(col3, '(') AS pos_open,
    instr(col3, ')') AS pos_close,
    instr(col1, ' ') AS pos1,
    instr(substr(col1, instr(col1, ' ')+1), ' ') AS pos2_rel
  FROM `table_1_1590967_7`
)
SELECT
  col0,
  col1,
  '`' || col2 || '`' AS col2,
  '`' || TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, 1, pos_open - 1)) || '`' AS `Musical Performer`,
  '`' || TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, pos_open + 1, pos_close - pos_open - 1)) || '`' AS `Song Performed`,
  col4,
  col5,
  printf(
    '%04d-%02d-%02d',
    CAST(TRIM(substr(col1, pos1 + pos2_rel + 1)) AS INTEGER),
    CASE TRIM(substr(col1, pos1 + 1, pos2_rel - 1))
      WHEN 'January' THEN 1 WHEN 'February' THEN 2 WHEN 'March' THEN 3 WHEN 'April' THEN 4
      WHEN 'May' THEN 5 WHEN 'June' THEN 6 WHEN 'July' THEN 7 WHEN 'August' THEN 8
      WHEN 'September' THEN 9 WHEN 'October' THEN 10 WHEN 'November' THEN 11 WHEN 'December' THEN 12
      ELSE 0 END,
    CAST(TRIM(substr(col1, 1, pos1 - 1)) AS INTEGER)
  ) AS `ISO Air Date`,
  COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, 1, pos_open - 1))) AS `Episodes by Musical Performer`,
  '`' || col1 || '` - `' || TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, 1, pos_open - 1)) || '` performing `' || TRIM(substr(`MusicalFull`, pos_open + 1, pos_close - pos_open - 1)) || '`' AS `Music Rights Reference`
FROM parsed
ORDER BY `ISO Air Date`;

nl: t.Seasons > s.Seasons AND s.Seasons >= 1 で表を自分自身に結合し,同時に"Project Runway Canada"と"Project Runway Malaysia"という空文字列の2つの列を返し, 国によってグループ化して,その COUNT t.Seasons) > 0 のグループだけを保持し,結果を10列に制限することで生成される"Seasons Above Peers"の"COUNT t.Seasons) はどれですか?
sql:
SELECT DISTINCT t.`Country`, COUNT(t.`Seasons`) `Seasons Above Peers`, '' `Project Runway Canada`, '' `Project Runway Malaysia`
FROM `table_1_1597866_3` t
JOIN `table_1_1597866_3` s
ON t.`Seasons` > s.`Seasons` AND s.`Seasons` >= 1
WHERE t.`Seasons` > 1
GROUP BY t.`Country`
HAVING COUNT(t.`Seasons`) > 0
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT t.col0, COUNT(t.col6) `Seasons Above Peers`, '' `Project Runway Canada`, '' `Project Runway Malaysia`
FROM `table_1_1597866_3` t
JOIN `table_1_1597866_3` s
ON t.col6 > s.col6 AND s.col6 >= 1
WHERE t.col6 > 1
GROUP BY t.col0
HAVING COUNT(t.col6) > 0
LIMIT 10;

nl: グループ加盟国 (欧州連合を除く) は,PPP US$ (2012) の人当たりのGDPが20000〜45000の間でFiscal Risk = "Public Debt % of GDP (2013 Q1) > 100の他の"Lower stress"で,PPP US$ (2012) の人当たりのGDPが最も近い整数に丸められ,PPP US$ (2012) の人当たりのGDPは平均全体に丸められ,PPP GDPの平均公共負債 % (2013 Q1) は10位に丸められ,ただ一つ以上のメンバーを持つグループのみを示している.
sql:
SELECT
  CASE WHEN `Public Debt % of GDP (2013 Q1)` > 100 THEN '`High fiscal stress`' ELSE '`Lower stress`' END AS `Fiscal Risk`,
  COUNT(*) `Members`,
  ROUND(AVG(`GDP per capita in PPP US$ (2012)`),0) `Avg GDPpc`,
  ROUND(AVG(`Public Debt % of GDP (2013 Q1)`),1) `Avg Debt`
FROM `table_1_1598533_8`
JOIN `table_1_1598533_8` ON 1=1
WHERE `Member State sorted by GDP` <> '`European Union`' AND `GDP per capita in PPP US$ (2012)` BETWEEN 20000 AND 45000
GROUP BY `Fiscal Risk`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
db_sql:
SELECT
  CASE WHEN col5 > 100 THEN 'High fiscal stress' ELSE 'Lower stress' END AS `Fiscal Risk`,
  COUNT(*) AS `Members`,
  ROUND(AVG(col4),0) AS `Avg GDPpc`,
  ROUND(AVG(col5),1) AS `Avg Debt`
FROM `table_1_1598533_8`
WHERE col0 <> 'European Union' AND col4 BETWEEN 20000 AND 45000
GROUP BY `Fiscal Risk`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;

nl: 視聴者 (数百万) が総平均視聴者 (avg_v) を上回るエピソードで,RUN時間は秒に変換され ((:' * 60) + ':' の後秒) が総平均RUN時間 (avg_s) を上回るエピソードでは,エピソード,放送日期,RUN時間,視聴者 (数百万),アーカイブ,およびpct_above_avgは, (Viewers (数百万)) / avg_v - 1 として定義され,視聴者 (数百万) が下降して5行に制限されるエピソード,放送日期,RUN時間は何ですか?
sql:
WITH `overall`(`avg_v`,`avg_s`) AS (
  SELECT AVG(`Viewers (in millions)`+0), AVG((substr(`Run time`,1,instr(`Run time`,':')-1)+0)*60 + (substr(`Run time`,instr(`Run time`,':')+1)+0))
  FROM `table_1_1601935_1`
)
SELECT `Episode`,`Broadcast date`,`Run time`,`Viewers (in millions)`,`Archive`,
       (`Viewers (in millions)`+0)/`avg_v`-1 `pct_above_avg`
FROM `table_1_1601935_1`,`overall`
WHERE (`Viewers (in millions)`+0) > `avg_v`
AND ((substr(`Run time`,1,instr(`Run time`,':')-1)+0)*60 + (substr(`Run time`,instr(`Run time`,':')+1)+0)) > `avg_s`
ORDER BY `Viewers (in millions)`+0 DESC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
WITH `overall`(`avg_v`,`avg_s`) AS (
  SELECT AVG(col3+0), AVG((substr(col2,1,instr(col2,':')-1)+0)*60 + (substr(col2,instr(col2,':')+1)+0))
  FROM `table_1_1601935_1`
)
SELECT col0, col1, col2, col3, col4,
       ((col3+0)/`avg_v` - 1) AS `pct_above_avg`
FROM `table_1_1601935_1`, `overall`
WHERE ((col3+0) > `avg_v`)
   OR (((substr(col2,1,instr(col2,':')-1)+0)*60 + (substr(col2,instr(col2,':')+1)+0)) > `avg_s`)
   AND 1=1
ORDER BY (col3+0) DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: チャンネル,ステーション,ネットワーク,ビデオ周波数,オーディオ周波数を使用して,ビデオ周波数とオーディオ周波数を"-MHz"とスペースを取り除くことで変換し,結果を数字として Video_freq と Audio_freq として処理し,ギャップを (Audio_freq - Video_freq) として計算し,テーブルの平均ギャップとして OverallAvg を計算します. その後 (1) "`MPB`"を除く各ネットワークに対して,ネットワーク, COUNT(Gap) をステーションとして,AVG(Gap) を AvgGap と MAX(Gap として MaxGap として,COUNT(Station) > 1 (制限 10),UNION (2) を DISTINCT ステーション,ネットワーク,ギャップ,および Video_q に返します.
sql:
WITH freqs AS (
  SELECT
    `Channel`,
    `Station`,
    `Network`,
    (REPLACE(REPLACE(`Video Frequency`, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0) `Video_freq`,
    (REPLACE(REPLACE(`Audio Frequency`, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0) `Audio_freq`,
    ((REPLACE(REPLACE(`Audio Frequency`, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0) - (REPLACE(REPLACE(`Video Frequency`, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0)) `Gap`
  FROM `table_1_160728_4`
),
stats AS (
  SELECT AVG(((REPLACE(REPLACE(`Audio Frequency`, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0) - (REPLACE(REPLACE(`Video Frequency`, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0))) `OverallAvg`
  FROM `table_1_160728_4`
)
SELECT `Network`, COUNT(`Station`) `Stations`, AVG(`Gap`) `AvgGap`, MAX(`Gap`) `MaxGap`
FROM freqs, stats
WHERE `Network` <> '`MPB`'
GROUP BY `Network`
HAVING COUNT(`Station`) > 1
LIMIT 10
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT `Station`, `Network`, `Gap`, `Video_freq`
FROM freqs
WHERE `Gap` > `OverallAvg` AND `Status` = '`Commercial`'
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
WITH freqs AS (
  SELECT
    col0,
    col4,
    col5,
    col8,
    (REPLACE(REPLACE(col2, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0) AS `Video_freq`,
    (REPLACE(REPLACE(col3, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0) AS `Audio_freq`,
    ((REPLACE(REPLACE(col3, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0) - (REPLACE(REPLACE(col2, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0)) AS `Gap`
  FROM `table_1_160728_4`
),
stats AS (
  SELECT AVG(((REPLACE(REPLACE(col3, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0) - (REPLACE(REPLACE(col2, '- MHz', ''), ' ', '') + 0))) AS `OverallAvg`
  FROM `table_1_160728_4`
)
SELECT col5, COUNT(col4) AS `Stations`, AVG(`Gap`) AS `AvgGap`, MAX(`Gap`) AS `MaxGap`
FROM freqs, stats
WHERE col5 <> 'MPB' AND col5 IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY col5
HAVING COUNT(col4) > 1
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT col4, col5, `Gap`, `Video_freq`
FROM freqs, stats
WHERE `Gap` > `OverallAvg` AND col8 = 'Commercial'
ORDER BY col5 DESC
LIMIT 10;

nl: プライマリー会議ごとに,プライマリー会議の名称,機関としての機関の数,SUM(登録) の合計登録,AVGのラウンド(登録) のAvg登録,およびセントラル・ワシントン大学のための明示的なゼロは 0,アイダホ大学のための0,ゴンザガ大学のための0,太平洋ルーサーン大学のための0,ポートランド大学のための0 ピュージェットサウンド大学,南オレゴン大学のための0 西オレゴン大学,ウェスタンワシントン大学のための0です.

nl: 乗り物と対応する national_g/mi (最初の文字から最初のスペースまでの"米国平均電気混合物"のサブストリングを INTEGERとキャスティングで定義する) は,下降順で national_g/mi で順番付けするとき,ただ単に 乗り物が空きでない行のみを考慮して,トップ結果を返します.
sql:
SELECT t1.`Vehicle`, CAST(substr(t1.`U.S. national average electric mix`,1,instr(t1.`U.S. national average electric mix`,' ')-1) AS INTEGER) `national_g/mi`
FROM `table_1_16105186_2` t1 JOIN `table_1_16105186_2` t2 ON 1=1
WHERE 1=1 AND t1.`Vehicle` <> ''
ORDER BY `national_g/mi` DESC LIMIT 1;
db_sql:
SELECT t1.col0, CAST(substr(t1.col6,1,instr(t1.col6,' ')-1) AS INTEGER) `national_g/mi`
FROM `table_1_16105186_2` t1 JOIN `table_1_16105186_2` t2 ON 1=1
WHERE 1=1 AND t1.col0 <> ''
ORDER BY `national_g/mi` DESC LIMIT 1;

nl: 標準課税総収益 (€百万) が前の財政年度 (前の財政年度) の標準課税総収益 (€百万) を上回る (年の最初の4桁を引いて,1を引いて,次に"-"と最後の2桁を連鎖して決定する) に対して,年報告,標準課税総収益 (€百万),GDP (% で),同年 % 変化 (% 円) を (現在 − 前) * 100.0 / 前) と計算し,インプリントGDP (€百万) を (% 円) で計算し,GDP (% 円) で割った標準課税総収益 (€百万) と計算し,トップ5の結果を示します.
sql:
SELECT t.`Year`, t.`Standard Duties Total Revenue (in €million)`, t.`over GDP (in %)`, ROUND((t.`Standard Duties Total Revenue (in €million)` - prev.`Standard Duties Total Revenue (in €million)`) * 100.0 / prev.`Standard Duties Total Revenue (in €million)`,2) `YoY % change`, ROUND(t.`Standard Duties Total Revenue (in €million)` / t.`over GDP (in %)`,2) `Implied GDP (in €million)`
FROM `table_1_1618358_1` t JOIN `table_1_1618358_1` prev ON prev.`Year` = ((substr(t.`Year`,1,4) - 1) || '-' || substr(t.`Year`,3,2))
WHERE t.`Standard Duties Total Revenue (in €million)` > prev.`Standard Duties Total Revenue (in €million)`
ORDER BY `YoY % change` DESC LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT t.col0, t.col3, t.col5, ROUND((t.col3 - prev.col3) * 100.0 / prev.col3,2) `YoY % change`, ROUND(t.col3 / t.col5,2) `Implied GDP (in €million)`
FROM `table_1_1618358_1` t JOIN `table_1_1618358_1` prev ON prev.col0 = ((substr(t.col0,1,4) - 1) || '-' || substr(t.col0,3,2))
WHERE t.col3 > prev.col3
ORDER BY `YoY % change` DESC LIMIT 5;

nl: ゲームログと WHERE 1=1を使用すると,各レコードのプロダクトは:レコード; COUNT(*) AS "Total Games"; ROUND(AVG(Attendance),0) AS "Avg Attendance"; ROUND(SUM(((((`at/vs.`='vs.') **Attendance)/NULLIF(SUM) /((((((`at/vs.`='vs.')),0),0) AS "Avg Home Attendance"; ROUNDAVG((((SubstrScore,1, - ') - 1) - +0) - (substr(Score,instrScore, - ') +3)),2) AS "Avgal"; + MAX'New England Diffzers'), 'Baltimore Thunder' (((((MAX' New York Goints), MAX'
sql:
WITH `GameLog`(`#`,`Date`,`at/vs.`,`Opponent`,`Score`,`Attendance`,`Record`) AS (
  VALUES
    (1,'January 14, 1989','vs.','New England Blazers','19 - 8',16269,'Win'),
    (2,'January 21, 1989','at','Baltimore Thunder','14 - 13',6479,'Win'),
    (3,'January 28, 1989','at','New York Saints','16 - 20',9324,'Loss'),
    (4,'February 12, 1989','vs.','Baltimore Thunder','14 - 9',12220,'Win'),
    (5,'February 18, 1989','vs.','Detroit Turbos','19 - 10',13932,'Win'),
    (6,'February 24, 1989','at','New England Blazers','16 - 11',8107,'Win'),
    (7,'March 4, 1989','at','Detroit Turbos','11 - 16',10637,'Loss'),
    (8,'March 10, 1989','vs.','Washington Wave','13 - 9',16413,'Win')
)
SELECT
  `Record`,
  COUNT(*) `Total Games`,
  ROUND(AVG(`Attendance`),0) `Avg Attendance`,
  ROUND(SUM((`at/vs.`='vs.')*`Attendance`)/NULLIF(SUM((`at/vs.`='vs.')),0),0) `Avg Home Attendance`,
  ROUND(AVG((substr(`Score`,1,instr(`Score`,' - ')-1)+0) - (substr(`Score`,instr(`Score`,' - ')+3)+0)),2) `Avg Goal Diff`,
  MAX('New England Blazers') `New England Blazers`,
  MAX('Baltimore Thunder') `Baltimore Thunder`,
  MAX('New York Saints') `New York Saints`,
  MAX('Detroit Turbos') `Detroit Turbos`,
  MAX('Washington Wave') `Washington Wave`
FROM `GameLog`
WHERE 1=1
GROUP BY `Record`
ORDER BY `Avg Attendance`*-1
LIMIT 10;

nl: プロヴィンス,国連地域,人口,面積 (km2),プロヴィンスの密度 ((人口*1.0) /地域 (km2)),および地域の avg_density (AVG(人口*1.0) /地域 (km2) を示す各州は,国連地域によって地域 (km2) >0と (人口*1.0) /地域 (km2) >= avg_densityを指定し,20列に制限されている地域 (km2) を含む地域 (州) と地域 (州) に結合した結果である.
sql:
WITH `regional_stats` AS (
  SELECT `U.N. Region`, AVG((`Population`*1.0)/`Area (km²)`) `avg_density`, SUM(`Population`) `total_pop`
  FROM `table_1_16278349_1`
  GROUP BY `U.N. Region`
)
SELECT DISTINCT t.`Province`, t.`U.N. Region`, t.`Population`, t.`Area (km²)`, (t.`Population`*1.0)/t.`Area (km²)` `density`, rs.`avg_density`
FROM `table_1_16278349_1` t NATURAL JOIN `regional_stats` rs
WHERE t.`Area (km²)` > 0 AND (t.`Population`*1.0)/t.`Area (km²)` >= rs.`avg_density`
ORDER BY `U.N. Region`
LIMIT 20;
db_sql:
WITH `regional_stats` AS (
  SELECT col8, AVG((col4*1.0)/col5) `avg_density`, SUM(col4) `total_pop`
  FROM `table_1_16278349_1`
  GROUP BY col8
)
SELECT DISTINCT t.col0, t.col8, t.col4, t.col5, (t.col4*1.0)/t.col5 `density`, rs.`avg_density`
FROM `table_1_16278349_1` t NATURAL JOIN `regional_stats` rs
WHERE t.col5 > 0 AND (t.col4*1.0)/t.col5 >= rs.`avg_density`
ORDER BY col8
LIMIT 20;

nl: 町村/村が少なくとも100個と面積 (km2) が5000未満の郡では, カウンティの名前, カウンティ座席,エリア (km2), 人口,人口密度,町村/村,町村ごとに地域 (エリア (km2) /町村/村),町村ごとに人口 (人口 /町村/村),人口密度デルタ (人口密度 - (人口 /面積 (km2)),および計算/報告比 ((人口 /面積 (km2) /人口密度) を返します.
sql: SELECT `Name of county`, `County seat`, `Area (km²)`, `Population`, `Population density`, `Towns/ villages`, (`Area (km²)` / `Towns/ villages`) AS `Area per town`, (`Population` / `Towns/ villages`) `Population per town`, ((`Population density`) - (`Population` / `Area (km²)`)) `Density delta`, ((`Population` / `Area (km²)`) / NULLIF(`Population density`,0)) `Computed/Reported ratio` FROM `table_1_16278825_1` WHERE `Towns/ villages` >= 100 AND `Area (km²)` < 5000 ORDER BY -(`Population` / `Towns/ villages`) LIMIT 5;
db_sql: SELECT col0, col1, col2, col3, col4, col5, (col2 / col5) AS `Area per town`, (col3 / col5) `Population per town`, ((col4) - (col3 / col2)) `Density delta`, ((col3 / col2) / NULLIF(col4,0)) `Computed/Reported ratio` FROM `table_1_16278825_1` WHERE col5 >= 100 AND col2 < 5000 ORDER BY -(col3 / col5) LIMIT 5;

nl: 各シリーズ (シリーズによってグループ) において,リリースが空の文字列ではなく称号が空の文字列でない記録のみを考慮すると,シリーズを報告し,タイトルを総タイトル (COUNT(称号) として数える,ライターを総ライター (COUNT(ライター) として数える,行数を長さ = '70' として数える,行数を長さ = '60' として数える,最新リリース日付 (MINリリース日) AS初リリース日 (MAXリリース日) AS最新リリース日 (UNリリース日) AS最新リリース,シリーズを1つ以上の称号 (HAVING) COUNTING号号と称号に数える,並べて10行まで含む.
sql:
SELECT `Series`, COUNT(`Title`) AS `Total Titles`, COUNT(`Writer`) `Total Writers`, SUM(`Length` = '70''' ) `Count 70'`, SUM(`Length` = '60''' ) `Count 60'`, MIN(`Release Date`) `Earliest Release`, MAX(`Release Date`) `Latest Release`
FROM `table_1_16279520_1`
WHERE `Release` <> '' AND `Title` <> ''
GROUP BY `Series`
HAVING COUNT(`Title`) > 1
ORDER BY `Total Titles`
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT col1, COUNT(col0) AS `Total Titles`, COUNT(col4) `Total Writers`, SUM(col6 = '70''' ) `Count 70'`, SUM(col6 = '60''' ) `Count 60'`, MIN(col8) `Earliest Release`, MAX(col8) `Latest Release`
FROM `table_1_16279520_1`
WHERE col2 <> '' AND col0 <> ''
GROUP BY col1
HAVING COUNT(col0) > 1
ORDER BY `Total Titles`
LIMIT 10;

nl: どの5年 (年"20"と"MDY"と"2008) の最後の2文字が連結された年"は グロス総売上高が最も高く,それらの5年ごとにどれが: グロス総売上高 ("$"と逗号を取り除いた後の合計),平均販売 (%) (%"を取り除いた後の平均),販売されたチケット総額 ("/"と逗号を取り除いた前の部分の総額),利用可能なチケット総額 ("/"と逗号を取り除いた部分の総額) と平均的な グロス総額 (行数に分けられた総額) ですか?
sql:
SELECT '20' || SUBSTR(`Dates (MDY)`, -2),
 SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(`Gross sales`,'$',''),',','')),
 AVG(REPLACE(`Sellout (%)`,'%','')),
 SUM(TRIM(REPLACE(SUBSTR(`Tickets sold / available`,1,INSTR(`Tickets sold / available`,'/')-1),',',''))),
 SUM(TRIM(REPLACE(SUBSTR(`Tickets sold / available`,INSTR(`Tickets sold / available`,'/')+1),',',''))),
 SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(`Gross sales`,'$',''),',',''))/COUNT(*)
FROM `table_1_16331025_2`
WHERE '20' || SUBSTR(`Dates (MDY)`, -2) >= '2008'
GROUP BY '20' || SUBSTR(`Dates (MDY)`, -2)
ORDER BY SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(`Gross sales`,'$',''),',','')) DESC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT '20' || SUBSTR(col0, -2),
 SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(col2,'$',''),',','')),
 AVG(REPLACE(col4,'%','')),
 SUM(TRIM(REPLACE(SUBSTR(col3,1,INSTR(col3,'/')-1),',',''))),
 SUM(TRIM(REPLACE(SUBSTR(col3,INSTR(col3,'/')+1),',',''))),
 SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(col2,'$',''),',',''))/COUNT(*)
FROM `table_1_16331025_2`
WHERE '20' || SUBSTR(col0, -2) >= '2008'
GROUP BY '20' || SUBSTR(col0, -2)
ORDER BY SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(col2,'$',''),',','')) DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: 2006年と2011年のランシング (LAN),デトロイト (DTW),グランド・ラピッド (GRR),石 (FNT),カラマゾ (AZO),サギナワ (MBS) の平均国内旅客料金値を用い,各空港の百分比変更 ((2011 - 2006) / 2006) *100はどれか.
sql:
WITH `raw`(`Year`, `Lansing (LAN)`, `Detroit (DTW)`, `Grand Rapids (GRR)`, `Flint (FNT)`, `Kalamazoo (AZO)`, `Saginaw (MBS)`) AS (
  VALUES
  ('`2006`','`$370.61`','`$322.83`','`$413.74`','`$298.89`','`$472.93`','`$441.26`'),
  ('`2007`','`$364.39`','`$307.29`','`$420.68`','`$281.37`','`$471.01`','`$441.08`'),
  ('`2008`','`$397.75`','`$334.18`','`$463.96`','`$314.89`','`$517.32`','`$481.39`'),
  ('`2009`','`$434.59`','`$313.67`','`$409.85`','`$275.23`','`$500.55`','`$434.69`'),
  ('`2010`','`$482.76`','`$353.75`','`$377.29`','`$298.40`','`$563.92`','`$470.47`'),
  ('`2011`','`$433.59`','`$378.55`','`$400.11`','`$334.90`','`$579.23`','`$474.77`')
)
SELECT `airport`, ((`v2011` - `v2006`) / NULLIF(`v2006`,0)) * 100 AS `pct_change`
FROM (
  SELECT '`Lansing (LAN)`' AS `airport`,
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Lansing (LAN)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2011`') AS `v2011`,
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Lansing (LAN)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2006`') AS `v2006`
  UNION ALL
  SELECT '`Detroit (DTW)`',
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Detroit (DTW)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2011`'),
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Detroit (DTW)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2006`')
  UNION ALL
  SELECT '`Grand Rapids (GRR)`',
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Grand Rapids (GRR)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2011`'),
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Grand Rapids (GRR)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2006`')
  UNION ALL
  SELECT '`Flint (FNT)`',
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Flint (FNT)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2011`'),
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Flint (FNT)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2006`')
  UNION ALL
  SELECT '`Kalamazoo (AZO)`',
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Kalamazoo (AZO)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2011`'),
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Kalamazoo (AZO)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2006`')
  UNION ALL
  SELECT '`Saginaw (MBS)`',
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Saginaw (MBS)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2011`'),
    (SELECT REPLACE(REPLACE(`Saginaw (MBS)`,'`',''),'$','') + 0 FROM `raw` WHERE `Year` = '`2006`')
)
ORDER BY `pct_change` DESC;

nl: どの5つの学校 (制限 5) は,そのアフィリエイト (AffMax) の最大入学率 (Enrollment) に等しい入学率 (Enrollment) を有し, 3000以上の入学率 (Enrollment) を有し,各返学学校,アフィリエイト,入学,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリエイト,アフィリ
sql:
SELECT * FROM (
 SELECT t.`School`, t.`Affiliation`, t.`Enrollment`,
   CASE WHEN t.`Enrollment` >= (SELECT AVG(`Enrollment`) FROM `table_1_16383772_1` WHERE `Affiliation` = t.`Affiliation`) THEN 'At_or_Above' ELSE 'Below' END AS `Status`,
   MAX(t.`Enrollment`) OVER (PARTITION BY t.`Affiliation`) AS `AffMax`
 FROM `table_1_16383772_1` AS t
) s
WHERE s.`Enrollment` = s.`AffMax` AND s.`Enrollment` > 3000
ORDER BY s.`Enrollment` DESC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT * FROM (
 SELECT t.col0, t.col3, t.col4,
   CASE WHEN t.col4 >= (SELECT AVG(col4) FROM `table_1_16383772_1` WHERE col3 = t.col3) THEN 'At_or_Above' ELSE 'Below' END AS `Status`,
   MAX(t.col4) OVER (PARTITION BY t.col3) AS `AffMax`
 FROM `table_1_16383772_1` AS t
) s
WHERE s.col4 = s.`AffMax` AND s.col4 > 3000
ORDER BY s.col4 DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: 最低3話を監督した監督 ("ディレクターによる") をリストし,それぞれにディレクター (ディレクター),監督されたエピソードの数 (エピソード),異なる"脚本による"名前 (ライター) の逗号別列をリストし,制作 符号範囲を MAX("制作 符号") - MIN("制作 符号") (コードラング) として計算する.
sql:
WITH `directors` AS (
 SELECT `Directed by`, COUNT(*) `EpisodeCount`
 FROM `table_1_16384596_4`
 GROUP BY `Directed by`
 HAVING `EpisodeCount` >= 3
)
SELECT `directors`.`Directed by` `Director`, `EpisodeCount` `Episodes`, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT `Written by`) `Writers`, MAX(`Production Code`) - MIN(`Production Code`) `CodeRange`
FROM `directors`
JOIN `table_1_16384596_4` USING (`Directed by`)
GROUP BY `directors`.`Directed by`
ORDER BY `Episodes` DESC
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
WITH `directors` AS (
 SELECT col3, COUNT(*) `EpisodeCount`
 FROM `table_1_16384596_4`
 GROUP BY col3
 HAVING `EpisodeCount` >= 3
)
SELECT `directors`.col3 `Director`, `EpisodeCount` `Episodes`, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT col4) `Writers`, MAX(col6) - MIN(col6) `CodeRange`
FROM `directors`
JOIN `table_1_16384596_4` USING (col3)
GROUP BY `directors`.col3
ORDER BY `Episodes` DESC
LIMIT 10;

nl: 各 Ground に対して, Crowd > 10000 のゲームのみを考慮し,Count の Grounds を含めてのみ,Count の Grounds は,Count の Ground,COUNT (COUNT(*) は,Avg の群れとして丸められた平均群れ (ROUND(AVG(Crowd))) は,最大幅 (家庭チームのスコアにおける括弧内数値とAway チームのスコア内括弧内数値の絶対差のMAX) は,Max幅として,Close のゲーム数 (その絶対差が <= 5) は,Avg の群れが上昇する順序で決まります.
sql:
SELECT
`Ground`,
COUNT(*) `Matches`,
ROUND(AVG(`Crowd`)) `Avg crowd`,
MAX(abs(
 (substr(`Home team score`, instr(`Home team score`, '(')+1, instr(`Home team score`, ')') - instr(`Home team score`, '(') -1)+0)
 -
 (substr(`Away team score`, instr(`Away team score`, '(')+1, instr(`Away team score`, ')') - instr(`Away team score`, '(') -1)+0)
)) `Max margin`,
SUM((abs(
 (substr(`Home team score`, instr(`Home team score`, '(')+1, instr(`Home team score`, ')') - instr(`Home team score`, '(') -1)+0)
 -
 (substr(`Away team score`, instr(`Away team score`, '(')+1, instr(`Away team score`, ')') - instr(`Away team score`, '(') -1)+0)
) <= 5)) `Close games`
FROM `table_1_16387953_1`
WHERE `Crowd` > 10000
GROUP BY `Ground`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Avg crowd` ASC;
db_sql:

col4,
COUNT(*) `Matches`,
ROUND(AVG(col5)) `Avg crowd`,
MAX(abs(
 (substr(col1, instr(col1, '(')+1, instr(col1, ')') - instr(col1, '(') -1)+0)
 -
 (substr(col3, instr(col3, '(')+1, instr(col3, ')') - instr(col3, '(') -1)+0)
)) `Max margin`,
SUM((abs(
 (substr(col1, instr(col1, '(')+1, instr(col1, ')') - instr(col1, '(') -1)+0)
 -
 (substr(col3, instr(col3, '(')+1, instr(col3, ')') - instr(col3, '(') -1)+0)
) <= 5)) `Close games`
FROM `table_1_16387953_1`
WHERE col5 > 10000
GROUP BY col4
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Avg crowd` ASC;

nl: `アウェーチーム`, `アウェーチーム`, `ホームポイント` (`ホームチームスコア`), `アウェーポイント` (`アウェーチームスコア`), `マージン` (これらの2つのポイント値間の絶対差異), そして ` Crowd` (マージン * 群) > 1500000で,1つの結果のみを返します.
sql: SELECT `Home team`, `Away team`, substr(`Home team score`, instr(`Home team score`,'(')+1, instr(`Home team score`,')') - instr(`Home team score`,'(') - 1) `Home Points`, substr(`Away team score`, instr(`Away team score`,'(')+1, instr(`Away team score`,')') - instr(`Away team score`,'(') - 1) `Away Points`, abs((substr(`Home team score`, instr(`Home team score`,'(')+1, instr(`Home team score`,')') - instr(`Home team score`,'(') - 1)+0) - (substr(`Away team score`, instr(`Away team score`,'(')+1, instr(`Away team score`,')') - instr(`Away team score`,'(') - 1)+0)) `Margin`, `Crowd` FROM `table_1_16388316_1` WHERE (abs((substr(`Home team score`, instr(`Home team score`,'(')+1, instr(`Home team score`,')') - instr(`Home team score`,'(') - 1)+0) - (substr(`Away team score`, instr(`Away team score`,'(')+1, instr(`Away team score`,')') - instr(`Away team score`,'(') - 1)+0)) * `Crowd`) > 1500000 LIMIT 1;
db_sql: SELECT col0, col2, substr(col1, instr(col1,'(')+1, instr(col1,')') - instr(col1,'(') - 1) `Home Points`, substr(col3, instr(col3,'(')+1, instr(col3,')') - instr(col3,'(') - 1) `Away Points`, abs((substr(col1, instr(col1,'(')+1, instr(col1,')') - instr(col1,'(') - 1)+0) - (substr(col3, instr(col3,'(')+1, instr(col3,')') - instr(col3,'(') - 1)+0)) `Margin`, col5 FROM `table_1_16388316_1` WHERE (abs((substr(col1, instr(col1,'(')+1, instr(col1,')') - instr(col1,'(') - 1)+0) - (substr(col3, instr(col3,'(')+1, instr(col3,')') - instr(col3,'(') - 1)+0)) * col5) > 1500000 LIMIT 1;

nl: グラウンドが空っぽではない家庭チームによってグループ化され, 家庭チーム, 試合がプレイされた (COUNT), 合計群衆 (群衆の合計), 平均群衆が0桁に丸められる (ROUND(AVG(Crowd),0) と, Max Crowd (MAX(Crowd) はどれですか?

SELECT `Home team`, COUNT(*) `Matches Played`, SUM(`Crowd`) `Total Crowd`, ROUND(AVG(`Crowd`),0) `Average Crowd`, MAX(`Crowd`) `Max Crowd`
FROM (VALUES
  ('Geelong','4.10 (34)','Sydney','6.11 (47)','Marrara Oval','Friday, 16 February',8500),
  ('Port Adelaide','16.25 (121)','Essendon','5.12 (42)','Football Park','Saturday, 17 February',19498),
  ('Port Adelaide','17.10 (112)','Sydney','15.17 (107)','Football Park','Friday, 23 February',15709),
  ('Essendon','12.18 (90)','Geelong','17.10 (112)','Colonial Stadium','Friday, 23 February',22829),
  ('Geelong','12.15 (87)','Port Adelaide','16.9 (105)','Colonial Stadium','Saturday, 3 March',4474)
) AS `t`(`Home team`,`Home team score`,`Away team`,`Away team score`,`Ground`,`Date`,`Crowd`)
WHERE `Ground` <> ''
GROUP BY `Home team`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Total Crowd` * -1
LIMIT 10;

nl: Week, デイト,Opponent,Game site,および 出席を指定し,最終スコアのサブストリングとしてチームポイントを計算します. キャラクター3から""直前に",Opponent points as the substring after "",Margin as (Opponent points - Team points),Opponent strings does not contain 'at' and 0 otherwise, and 出席 per margin equal to 出席 divided by (Margin + 1), 出席=10000と計算された Margin=10の行のみを含む.
sql:
SELECT
`Week`,
`Date`,
`Opponent`,
`Game site`,
`Attendance`,
((substr(`Final score`, instr(`Final score`, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(`Final score`, 3, instr(`Final score`, '–') - 3) * 1)) `Margin`,
((substr(`Final score`, 3, instr(`Final score`, '–') - 3) * 1)) `Team points`,
((substr(`Final score`, instr(`Final score`, '–')+1) * 1)) `Opponent points`,
((instr(`Opponent`, 'at ') = 0) * 1) `Home flag`,
(`Attendance` / (((substr(`Final score`, instr(`Final score`, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(`Final score`, 3, instr(`Final score`, '–') - 3) * 1) + 1))) `Attendance per margin`
FROM `table_1_1639689_2`
WHERE `Attendance` >= 10000 AND (((substr(`Final score`, instr(`Final score`, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(`Final score`, 3, instr(`Final score`, '–') - 3) * 1)) >= 10);

col6,
col7,
((substr(col4, instr(col4, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(col4, 3, instr(col4, '–') - 3) * 1)) `Margin`,
((substr(col4, 3, instr(col4, '–') - 3) * 1)) `Team points`,
((substr(col4, instr(col4, '–')+1) * 1)) `Opponent points`,
((instr(col3, 'at ') = 0) * 1) `Home flag`,
(col7 / (((substr(col4, instr(col4, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(col4, 3, instr(col4, '–') - 3) * 1) + 1))) `Attendance per margin`
FROM `table_1_1639689_2`
WHERE col7 >= 10000 AND (((substr(col4, instr(col4, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(col4, 3, instr(col4, '–') - 3) * 1)) >= 10);

nl: 同じホームリンクを共有し,機関 A <機関 B を満たしている機関 (機関 A と機関 B) のペアを提供し,機関 A,機関 B,ホームリンクを表示し,A の登録がB の登録よりも大きいかどうかによって"A より大きい" /"B より大きい" /"等しい"と記された登録比較を提供し,A の登録がB の登録よりも大きいか/少なくか/等しいかによって,およびA (会議 A) とB (会議 B) のプライマリー会議を表示し,ホームリンクによって注文され,最初に"A より大きい"と登録比較によって上昇し,結果100に制限されます.
sql: SELECT b1.`Institution` AS `Institution A`, b2.`Institution` AS `Institution B`, b1.`Home Rink`, CASE WHEN b1.`Enrollment` > b2.`Enrollment` THEN 'A larger' WHEN b1.`Enrollment` < b2.`Enrollment` THEN 'B larger' ELSE 'Equal' END AS `Enrollment comparison`, b1.`Primary conference` AS `Conference A`, b2.`Primary conference` AS `Conference B` FROM `table_1_16403890_1` b1 INNER JOIN `table_1_16403890_1` b2 ON b1.`Home Rink` = b2.`Home Rink` AND b1.`Institution` < b2.`Institution` WHERE b1.`Institution` IS b1.`Institution` ORDER BY `Home Rink` ASC, `Enrollment comparison` DESC LIMIT 100;
db_sql: SELECT DISTINCT b1.col0 AS `Institution A`, b2.col0 AS `Institution B`, b1.col7 AS col7, CASE WHEN b1.col4 > b2.col4 THEN 'A larger' WHEN b1.col4 < b2.col4 THEN 'B larger' ELSE 'Equal' END AS `Enrollment comparison` FROM `table_1_16403890_1` AS b1 INNER JOIN `table_1_16403890_1` AS b2 ON b1.col7 = b2.col7 AND b1.col0 < b2.col0 WHERE b1.col0 IS NOT NULL GROUP BY b1.col7, b1.col0, b2.col0 HAVING COUNT(*) >= 1 ORDER BY b1.col7 ASC, `Enrollment comparison` DESC LIMIT 100 OFFSET 0;
db_result: [('duke university', 'university of north carolina', 'triangle sports plex', 'B larger')]

nl: 5 までの結果については,文字通り"レキシントン",学年,Lexington_Appearances"を総数として計算する. 1=1 OR 0=1 THEN ((Volleyball LIKE '%レキシントン%') + ( Cross Country LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Football LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Tennis LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Golf LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Basketball LIKE '%レキシントン%) + (Swimming LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Softball LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Track & フィールド LIKE '% Lex Lex Lexiントン%'D) 各学年 (Volleyball LIKE '%レキシントン%') に関する各学年 (Volleyball LIKE '%レキシントン%') に関する各学
sql: SELECT '`Lexington`', `School Year`, SUM(CASE WHEN 1=1 OR 0=1 THEN ((`Volleyball` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Cross Country` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Soccer` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Tennis` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Golf` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Basketball` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Swimming` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Softball` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Track & Field` LIKE '%Lexington%')) END) AS `Lexington_Appearances` FROM `table_1_16423070_4` WHERE ((`Volleyball` || `Cross Country` || `Soccer` || `Tennis` || `Golf` || `Basketball` || `Swimming` || `Softball` || `Track & Field`) LIKE '%Lexington%') AND 1=1 GROUP BY `School Year` HAVING `Lexington_Appearances` > 0 ORDER BY `Lexington_Appearances` LIMIT 5;
db_sql: SELECT '`Lexington`', col0, SUM(CASE WHEN 1=1 OR 0=1 THEN ((col1 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col2 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col3 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col4 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col5 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col6 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col7 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col8 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col9 LIKE '%Lexington%')) END) AS `Lexington_Appearances` FROM `table_1_16423070_4` WHERE ((col1 || col2 || col3 || col4 || col5 || col6 || col7 || col8 || col9) LIKE '%Lexington%') AND 1=1 GROUP BY col0 HAVING `Lexington_Appearances` > 0 ORDER BY `Lexington_Appearances` LIMIT 5;

nl: `Directed by ` (COUNT(*) の値は,シーズンで `No. との列の中で1以上のエピソード (HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) を含む.そして,それぞれに `Directed by `返信する `Directed by `名, `Episodes directed ` (COUNT(*) とのエピソード数, MIN(`Original air date`) を `First air date`,そして MAX(`Original air date`) を `Last air date`, output を `Episodes directed `下回順序で?
sql:
SELECT `Directed by`, COUNT(*) `Episodes directed`, MIN(`Original air date`) `First air date`, MAX(`Original air date`) `Last air date`
FROM `table_1_16432167_1`
WHERE `No. in season`>0
GROUP BY `Directed by`
HAVING COUNT(*)>1
ORDER BY `Episodes directed` DESC;
db_sql:
SELECT col3, COUNT(*) `Episodes directed`, MIN(col5) `First air date`, MAX(col5) `Last air date`
FROM `table_1_16432167_1`
WHERE col1>0
GROUP BY col3
HAVING COUNT(*)>1
ORDER BY `Episodes directed` DESC;

nl: 銃は m/v ft/s と マックス.高度 (ft) の両方で打っている.それぞれの銃を Better_than_peers (他の銃のカウント) に, Avg_Delta_v (この銃の m/v ft/s を引いて他の銃を引いて) に, Avg_Delta_25 (この銃の Time to ft (m) を 25° (秒) を引いて他の銃を引いて) に, Avg_Delta_h (この銃の マックス.高度 (ft) を引いて) に, Avg_Delta_v (下降) にのみトップ5の銃を返す.
sql:
SELECT t.`Gun`, COUNT(*) AS `Better_than_peers`, AVG(t.`m/v ft/s` - t2.`m/v ft/s`) `Avg_Delta_v`, AVG((t.`Time to ft (m) at 25° (seconds)`+0.0) - (t2.`Time to ft (m) at 25° (seconds)`+0.0)) `Avg_Delta_25`, AVG(t.`Max. height (ft)` - t2.`Max. height (ft)`) `Avg_Delta_h`
FROM `table_1_16439764_1` t
INNER JOIN `table_1_16439764_1` t2 ON t.`Gun` <> t2.`Gun`
WHERE (t.`m/v ft/s` > t2.`m/v ft/s`) AND (t.`Max. height (ft)` > t2.`Max. height (ft)`)
GROUP BY t.`Gun`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Avg_Delta_v` DESC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT t.col0, COUNT(*) AS `Better_than_peers`, AVG(t.col1 - t2.col1) `Avg_Delta_v`, AVG((t.col3+0.0) - (t2.col3+0.0)) `Avg_Delta_25`, AVG(t.col6 - t2.col6) `Avg_Delta_h`
FROM `table_1_16439764_1` t
INNER JOIN `table_1_16439764_1` t2 ON t.col0 <> t2.col0
WHERE (t.col1 > t2.col1) AND (t.col6 > t2.col6)
GROUP BY t.col0
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Avg_Delta_v` DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: 複数の選択肢を持つ大学を教えて下さい ポジションは数値で 1998年のCFLドラフトからBCのラウンド5の選択肢です
sql:
SELECT
  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(`College`, '; ')
   FROM (
     SELECT `College`
     FROM `table_1_16441561_5`
     GROUP BY `College`
     HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
     ORDER BY `College`
   )
  ) AS `Colleges with multiple picks`,
  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(`Position` || ':' || cnt, '; ')
   FROM (
     SELECT `Position`, COUNT(*) AS cnt
     FROM `table_1_16441561_5`
     GROUP BY `Position`
     ORDER BY cnt DESC, `Position`
   )
  ) AS `Position distribution (Position:Count)`,
  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(detail, '; ')
   FROM (
     SELECT 'Pick #' || `Pick #` || ' - ' || `Player` || ' (' || `Position` || ', ' || `College` || ')' AS detail
     FROM `table_1_16441561_5`
     WHERE `CFL Team` = 'B.C.'
     ORDER BY `Pick #`
   )
  ) AS `Picks by B.C.`;
db_sql:
SELECT
  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(col4, '; ')
   FROM (
     SELECT col4
     FROM `table_1_16441561_5`
     GROUP BY col4
     HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
     ORDER BY col4
   )
  ) AS `Colleges with multiple picks`,
  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(col3 || ':' || cnt, '; ')
   FROM (
     SELECT col3, COUNT(*) AS cnt
     FROM `table_1_16441561_5`
     GROUP BY col3
     ORDER BY cnt DESC, col3
   )
  ) AS `Position distribution (Position:Count)`,
  (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(detail, '; ')
   FROM (
     SELECT 'Pick #' || col0 || ' - ' || col2 || ' (' || col3 || ', ' || col4 || ')' AS detail
     FROM `table_1_16441561_5`
     WHERE col1 = 'B.C.'
     ORDER BY col0
   )
  ) AS `Picks by B.C.`;

nl: 各チーム (ローカルとスキップ) をW >=6でリストし,W,L,PF,PA,ポイント差=PF - PA,ゲームごとに差= (PF - PA) /(W + L) を2桁に丸め,エンドネット=エンド・ウィン -エンド・ウィン,ショット比率=ショット %を01比率に丸め,3桁に丸め,ストールシェア=ストールエンド/ (エンド・ウィン +エンド・ウィン) を3桁に丸め.

年間,ドライバーとメーカーを使用し,掃除後 `平均速度 (mph) ` 逗号を取り除いて数値の"`avg_spd`"と処理し,任意の"*"とスペースを取り除いて数値として処理し,合計結果は: (a) COUNT(*) > 1 でドライバーがエンティティ,Wins, AVGavg_spd) として3桁に丸められ AvgSpeed,MAX(avg_spd) として3桁に丸められ PeakSpeed,Type = 'driver' として3桁に丸められ,その avg_spd が MAX に等しいドライバー列を表示し,および (b) 製造者によるTUNT) > 1桁のWins,Wins, AVGavg_spd) として3桁に丸められ Avg_Speed,Avg
sql:
WITH `cleaned` AS (
 SELECT
  `Year`,
  `Driver`,
  `Manufacturer`,
  REPLACE(`Average speed (mph)`, ',', '') + 0.0 `avg_spd`,
  REPLACE(REPLACE(`Laps`, '*',''), ' ', '') + 0 `laps`
 FROM `table_1_16493961_1`
 WHERE `Average speed (mph)` IS NOT NULL
),
`driver_stats` AS (
 SELECT
  `Driver`,
  COUNT(*) `wins`,
  AVG(`avg_spd`) `avg_speed`,
  MAX(`avg_spd`) `max_speed`
 FROM `cleaned`
 GROUP BY `Driver`
 HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
)
SELECT DISTINCT
 ds.`Driver` `Entity`,
 ds.`wins` `Wins`,
 ROUND(ds.`avg_speed`,3) `AvgSpeed`,
 ROUND(ds.`max_speed`,3) `PeakSpeed`,
 'Driver' `Type`
FROM `driver_stats` ds
INNER JOIN `cleaned` c ON c.`Driver` = ds.`Driver` AND c.`avg_spd` = ds.`max_speed`
UNION ALL
SELECT DISTINCT
 `Manufacturer` `Entity`,
 COUNT(*) `Wins`,
 ROUND(AVG(`avg_spd`),3) `AvgSpeed`,
 MAX(`avg_spd`) `PeakSpeed`,
 'Manufacturer' `Type`
FROM `cleaned`
GROUP BY `Manufacturer`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY `Wins` DESC, `AvgSpeed` DESC
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT col2 AS `Entity`, COUNT(*) AS `Wins`, ROUND(AVG(REPLACE(col8, ',', '') + 0.0),3) AS `AvgSpeed`, MAX(REPLACE(col8, ',', '') + 0.0) AS `PeakSpeed`, 'Driver' AS `Type`
FROM `table_1_16493961_1`
WHERE col8 IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY col2
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
UNION ALL
SELECT col4, COUNT(*), 0, 0, 'Manufacturer'
FROM `table_1_16493961_1`
GROUP BY col4
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY `Wins` DESC, `AvgSpeed` DESC
LIMIT 10;

nl: 年代によってデータをグループ化し,その年代は任命された大司教の最後の4文字から決定される (その年 < '1900'は"1900以前"または"1900年代"と呼ぶ場合);各年代には,ERAのラベル, COUNT(Archbishop) と (substr(Vacated throne,-4,4) 減 (substr(Appointed Archbishop,-4,4)) の平均を年間平均任期として返し,最大10行まで返します.
sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN substr(`Appointed Archbishop`, -4, 4) < '1900' THEN 'Before 1900' ELSE '1900s' END `Era`, COUNT(`Archbishop`) `CountArchbishops`, AVG(substr(`Vacated throne`, -4, 4) - substr(`Appointed Archbishop`, -4, 4)) `AvgTenureYears`
FROM `table_1_1656555_1`
GROUP BY `Era`
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN substr(col4, -4, 4) < '1900' THEN 'Before 1900' ELSE '1900s' END `Era`, COUNT(col0) `CountArchbishops`, AVG(substr(col5, -4, 4) - substr(col4, -4, 4)) `AvgTenureYears`
FROM `table_1_1656555_1`
GROUP BY `Era`
LIMIT 10;

nl: 長さ (m) > 0 の列のみを考慮すると,ペーブメントの各タイプに対して,合計_長さ = SUM (長さ (m)), avg_climb = AVG (%)),およびカウント = COUNT (COUNT) を計算すると,難度_スコア = (総_長さ * avg_climb / 100.0) を計算する. DESC (type, total_length, avg_climb, count, and difficulty_score) を注文したときにどちらのペーブメントタイプが最大の難度_スコアを持っているのか?
sql:
WITH `pavements` AS (
  SELECT `Pavement` AS `type`, SUM(`Length (m)`) AS `total_length`, AVG(`Average climb (%)`) AS `avg_climb`, COUNT(*) AS `count`
  FROM `table_1_16654785_2`
  WHERE `Length (m)` > 0
  GROUP BY `Pavement`
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
)
SELECT `type`, `total_length`, `avg_climb`, `count`, (`total_length` * `avg_climb` / 100.0) AS `difficulty_score`
FROM `pavements`
ORDER BY `difficulty_score` DESC
LIMIT 2;
db_sql:
WITH `pavements` AS (
  SELECT col3 AS `type`, SUM(col4) AS `total_length`, AVG(col5) AS `avg_climb`, COUNT(*) AS `count`
  FROM `table_1_16654785_2`
  WHERE col4 > 0
  GROUP BY col3
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
)
SELECT `type`, `total_length`, `avg_climb`, `count`, (`total_length` * `avg_climb` / 100.0) AS `difficulty_score`
FROM `pavements`
ORDER BY `difficulty_score` DESC
LIMIT 2;

nl: [Na + ](mmol/L) > 0 と [Glucose](mmol/L) >= 0 のエントリについては, (2 * [Na + ](mmol/L) + [Glucose](mmol/L)) <= 295 と "Non-アイソトニック"でない場合は",アイソトニック"と分類する.
sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN (2*`[Na + ](mmol/L)` + `[Glucose](mmol/L)`) <= 295 THEN 'Isotonic' ELSE 'Non-Isotonic' END AS `Classification`, COUNT(*) `D5W`, AVG(`[Na + ](mmol/L)`)
FROM `table_1_16689223_1`
WHERE (`[Na + ](mmol/L)` > 0 AND `[Glucose](mmol/L)` >= 0)
GROUP BY 1
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
LIMIT 3;
db_sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN (2*col2 + col4) <= 295 THEN 'Isotonic' ELSE 'Non-Isotonic' END AS `Classification`, COUNT(*) `D5W`, AVG(col2)
FROM `table_1_16689223_1`
WHERE (col2 > 0 AND col4 >= 0)
GROUP BY 1
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
LIMIT 3;

nl: どの5つのチーム (LIMIT 5) は,合計レース,合計勝利,合計ポディウム,合計ポディウム,および勝利率=ROUND((SUM(WINS)*1.0)/NULLIF(SUM(Races),0),3) を含む合計レース,合計勝利,合計勝利,合計勝利,合計勝利,合計勝利,DESCによって注文されたシーズンを含む,レース >0と空きPTSを含む列のみを選択する?
sql: SELECT `Team`, SUM(`Races`) AS `Total Races`, SUM(`Wins`) AS `Total Wins`, SUM(`Podiums`) AS `Total Podiums`, ROUND((SUM(`Wins`)*1.0)/NULLIF(SUM(`Races`),0),3) AS `Win Rate`, '`2005`,`2006`,`2007`,`2008`,`2009`,`2010`,`2011`,`2012`,`2013`' AS `Seasons Included` FROM `table_1_16710541_2` WHERE `Races` > 0 AND `Pts` <> '' GROUP BY `Team` ORDER BY `Total Wins` DESC LIMIT 5;
db_sql: SELECT col2, SUM(col5) AS `Total Races`, SUM(col6) AS `Total Wins`, SUM(col7) AS `Total Podiums`, ROUND((SUM(col6)*1.0)/NULLIF(SUM(col5),0),3) AS `Win Rate`, '`2005`,`2006`,`2007`,`2008`,`2009`,`2010`,`2011`,`2012`,`2013`' AS `Seasons Included` FROM `table_1_16710541_2` WHERE col5 > 0 AND col10 <> '' GROUP BY col2 ORDER BY `Total Wins` DESC LIMIT 5;

nl: IsWinが決まった場合 WHEN `Falcons points` > `Opponents` THEN 1 ELSE 0 END,各 IsWin the Games (COUNT(*)), Wins (SUM(IsWin)), Avg_Attendance (AVG(`Attendance`)),および Max_Margin (MAX(`Falcons points` - `Opponents`) に対して報告し,Winsによって順序を下げる?
sql:
SELECT
  `IsWin`,
  COUNT(*) AS `Games`,
  SUM(`IsWin`) AS `Wins`,
  AVG(`Attendance`) AS `Avg_Attendance`,
  MAX(`Falcons points` - `Opponents`) AS `Max_Margin`
FROM (
  SELECT *,
    CASE WHEN `Falcons points` > `Opponents` THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS `IsWin`
  FROM `table_1_16710971_2`
)
GROUP BY `IsWin`
ORDER BY `Wins` DESC;
db_sql:
SELECT
  `IsWin`,
  COUNT(*) AS `Games`,
  SUM(`IsWin`) AS `Wins`,
  AVG(col7) AS `Avg_Attendance`,
  MAX(col4 - col5) AS `Max_Margin`
FROM (
  SELECT *,
    CASE WHEN col4 > col5 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS `IsWin`
  FROM `table_1_16710971_2`
)
GROUP BY `IsWin`
ORDER BY `Wins` DESC;

nl: チーム (s) により,総スタート (SUM(Starts) を,総勝利 (SUM(Wins) を,勝利割合を (SUM(Wins)*1.0)/SUM(SUM)*100を2桁まで丸め,平均 Avg. 2桁まで丸め,総勝利を"$"と""を剥がした後に丸め,0桁まで丸め (Ken Schrader Racing) と,MIN(Year) とMAXYear を,スタート >0の行のみを使用し,SUM(Starts) >=5を表示したチームのみを返します.
sql:
SELECT `Team(s)`, SUM(`Starts`), SUM(`Wins`), ROUND((SUM(`Wins`)*1.0)/SUM(`Starts`)*100,2), ROUND(AVG(`Avg. Finish` + 0),2), ROUND(SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(`Winnings`,'$',''),',','') + 0),0) AS `Ken Schrader Racing`, MIN(`Year`), MAX(`Year`)
FROM `table_1_1671401_2`
WHERE `Starts` > 0
GROUP BY `Team(s)`
HAVING SUM(`Starts`) >= 5
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT col10, SUM(col1), SUM(col2), ROUND((SUM(col2)*1.0)/SUM(col1)*100,2), ROUND(AVG(col7 + 0),2), ROUND(SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(col8,'$',''),',','') + 0),0) AS `Ken Schrader Racing`, MIN(col0), MAX(col0)
FROM `table_1_1671401_2`
WHERE col1 > 0
GROUP BY col10
HAVING SUM(col1) >= 5
LIMIT 10;

nl: どちらの5つのACCチームが参加者数が10000を超えた試合から,最も高いSUM (参加者数) を得ているか.各ACCチームにとって,COUNT (参加者数) とSUM (参加者数) はどれですか?
sql:
SELECT `ACC Team`, COUNT(`Attendance`), SUM(`Attendance`)
FROM `table_1_1672976_5`
WHERE `Attendance` > 10000
GROUP BY `ACC Team`
ORDER BY SUM(`Attendance`) DESC

nl: 最大10のソケットグループではソケットを返します. total_modelsを数え,平均TDP (avg_tdp) を返します.ここで avg_tdp は TDP から 'W' のサフィックスを取り除いて数に変換され,平均Mult. (avg_mult) を返します.ここで avg_mult は Mult. から '×' の文字を取り除いて数に変換され,最大 リリース価格 (max_price) と最小 リリース価格 (min_price) は,それぞれの価格が リリース価格 (USD) から '$' を取り除いて計算され,リリース価格 (USD) が '$) を含む場合にのみ考慮されます.
sql:
SELECT DISTINCT `Socket`,
       COUNT(*) "total_models",
       AVG(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') + 0.0) "avg_tdp",
       AVG(REPLACE(`Mult.`, '×', '') + 0.0) "avg_mult",
       MAX((REPLACE(`Release price ( USD )`, '$', '') + 0.0) * (INSTR(`Release price ( USD )`, '$') > 0)) "max_price",
       MIN((REPLACE(`Release price ( USD )`, '$', '') + 0.0) * (INSTR(`Release price ( USD )`, '$') > 0)) "min_price"
FROM `table_1_16729930_11`
WHERE LENGTH(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '')) > 0 AND LENGTH(REPLACE(`Mult.`, '×', '')) > 0
GROUP BY `Socket`
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT col8,
       COUNT(*) "total_models",
       AVG(REPLACE(col7, ' W', '') + 0.0) "avg_tdp",
       AVG(REPLACE(col5, '×', '') + 0.0) "avg_mult",
       MAX((REPLACE(col11, '$', '') + 0.0) * (INSTR(col11, '$') > 0)) "max_price",
       MIN((REPLACE(col11, '$', '') + 0.0) * (INSTR(col11, '$') > 0)) "min_price"
FROM `table_1_16729930_11`
WHERE LENGTH(REPLACE(col7, ' W', '')) > 0 AND LENGTH(REPLACE(col5, '×', '')) > 0
GROUP BY col8
LIMIT 10;

nl: 私の熱学彫刻では,TDP ≤4Wと電圧0.81.175Vの 45nm 原子をリストして,モデル,sSpec,部品番号,ソケット,発売日と価格,数値 TDPと1ソケット分/マックスと範囲,MHzでCPUとGPU周波数とその絶対デルタ,そしてどのモデルが各ソケットを共有するか,一番安いのは?
sql:
SELECT
  `Model number`,
  `sSpec number`,
  `Part number(s)`,
  `Socket`,
  `Release date`,
  `Release price ( USD )`,
  CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS REAL) AS `tdp_w`,
  MIN(CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS REAL)) OVER (PARTITION BY `Socket`) AS `min_tdp_socket`,
  MAX(CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS REAL)) OVER (PARTITION BY `Socket`) AS `max_tdp_socket`,
  (MAX(CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS REAL)) OVER (PARTITION BY `Socket`) - MIN(CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS REAL)) OVER (PARTITION BY `Socket`)) AS `tdp_range_w`,
  `Voltage`,
  CASE WHEN `Frequency` LIKE '%GHz' THEN CAST(REPLACE(`Frequency`, ' GHz', '') AS REAL)*1000 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(`Frequency`, ' MHz', '') AS REAL) END AS `cpu_mhz`,
  CASE WHEN `GPU frequency` LIKE '%GHz' THEN CAST(REPLACE(`GPU frequency`, ' GHz', '') AS REAL)*1000 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(`GPU frequency`, ' MHz', '') AS REAL) END AS `gpu_mhz`,
  ABS(
    (CASE WHEN `Frequency` LIKE '%GHz' THEN CAST(REPLACE(`Frequency`, ' GHz', '') AS REAL)*1000 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(`Frequency`, ' MHz', '') AS REAL) END)
    -
    (CASE WHEN `GPU frequency` LIKE '%GHz' THEN CAST(REPLACE(`GPU frequency`, ' GHz', '') AS REAL)*1000 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(`GPU frequency`, ' MHz', '') AS REAL) END)
  ) AS `abs_delta_mhz`,
  COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY `Socket`) AS `models_same_socket`,
  CAST(REPLACE(`Release price ( USD )`, '$', '') AS REAL) AS `price_usd`
FROM `table_1_16729930_17`
WHERE CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS REAL) <= 4
  AND `Voltage` = '0.8–1.175V'
ORDER BY `price_usd` ASC;
db_sql:
SELECT
  col0,
  col8,
  col7,
  col12,
  col9,
  col10,
  CASE WHEN col2 LIKE '%GHz' THEN CAST(REPLACE(col2, ' GHz', '') AS REAL)*1000 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(col2, ' MHz', '') AS REAL) END AS cpu_mhz,
  CASE WHEN col3 LIKE '%GHz' THEN CAST(REPLACE(col3, ' GHz', '') AS REAL)*1000 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(col3, ' MHz', '') AS REAL) END AS gpu_mhz,
  ABS(
    (CASE WHEN col2 LIKE '%GHz' THEN CAST(REPLACE(col2, ' GHz', '') AS REAL)*1000 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(col2, ' MHz', '') AS REAL) END)
    -
    (CASE WHEN col3 LIKE '%GHz' THEN CAST(REPLACE(col3, ' GHz', '') AS REAL)*1000 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(col3, ' MHz', '') AS REAL) END)
  ) AS abs_delta_mhz,
  CAST(REPLACE(col12, '$', '') AS REAL) AS price_usd
FROM `table_1_16729930_17`
WHERE CAST(REPLACE(col8, ' W', '') AS REAL) <= 3.6
  AND col7 LIKE '0.8%'
ORDER BY price_usd ASC;

nl: 屋根上での適性フラグを最初に表示する航空機 (報告されたディスク負荷 ≤ 5 lb/ft2), Pa の上昇で報告されたディスク負荷によって順序付けされ,計算されたディスク負荷,報告されたディスク負荷, Pa の両方,および絶対的および百分比の差異を記載し,異常値を強調する.
sql:
WITH `parsed` AS (
  SELECT
    `Aircraft`,
    `Description`,
    CAST(REPLACE(substr(`Max Gross Weight`, 1, instr(`Max Gross Weight`, ' ')-1), ',', '') AS REAL) AS `gross_lb`,
    CAST(REPLACE(substr(`Total disk area`, 1, instr(`Total disk area`, ' ')-1), ',', '') AS REAL) AS `disk_ft2`,
    CAST(REPLACE(substr(`Max disk Loading`, 1, instr(`Max disk Loading`, ' ')-1), ',', '') AS REAL) AS `reported_disk_lb_per_ft2`
  FROM `table_m_1764881136807_3c805f9f_10006830_1`
)
SELECT
  `Aircraft`,
  `Description`,
  `gross_lb`,
  `disk_ft2`,
  ROUND(`gross_lb` / NULLIF(`disk_ft2`, 0), 2) AS `computed_disk_lb_per_ft2`,
  `reported_disk_lb_per_ft2`,
  ROUND(`reported_disk_lb_per_ft2` * (4.44822 / 0.092903), 2) AS `reported_disk_Pa`,
  ROUND((`gross_lb` / NULLIF(`disk_ft2`, 0)) * (4.44822 / 0.092903), 2) AS `computed_disk_Pa`,
  ROUND(ABS((`gross_lb` / NULLIF(`disk_ft2`, 0)) - `reported_disk_lb_per_ft2`), 2) AS `abs_diff_lb_per_ft2`,
  ROUND(ABS(((`gross_lb` / NULLIF(`disk_ft2`, 0)) - `reported_disk_lb_per_ft2`) / NULLIF(`reported_disk_lb_per_ft2`, 0)) * 100, 2) AS `abs_diff_pct`,
  CASE WHEN `reported_disk_lb_per_ft2` <= 5.0 THEN 'candidate_for_rooftop' ELSE 'not_candidate' END AS `rooftop_suitability`
FROM `parsed`
ORDER BY CASE WHEN `reported_disk_lb_per_ft2` <= 5.0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END, `reported_disk_Pa` ASC, `abs_diff_lb_per_ft2` DESC;

nl: ポジションに"ガード"または"フォワード"が含まれている列に限定された各国籍ごとに,合計プレイヤー (COUNT(*) を,最初の開始年" トロントにおける年"の最初の4文字を数値として使用する (MIN(substr(" トロントにおける年",1,4)+0) を,平均的な開始年を10位に丸める (ROUND(AVG(substr(" トロントにおける年",1,4)+0),1) を,ポジションにおける"ガード"のエントリの数を,ポジションにおける"ガード"のエントリの数 (SUM(( LIKE "%Guard%") を,ポジションにおける"フォワード"のカウント (SUMポジションにおける"% LIKE "Forward%") を,そして2005年開始前に"確立された"というコアートコラムを表す.
sql:
SELECT `Nationality` AS `Nationality`,
       COUNT(*) `Players`,
       MIN(substr(`Years in Toronto`,1,4)+0) `EarliestStart`,
       ROUND(AVG(substr(`Years in Toronto`,1,4)+0),1) `AverageStart`,
       SUM(`Position` LIKE '%Guard%') `Guard`,
       SUM(`Position` LIKE '%Forward%') `Forward`,
       CASE WHEN MIN(substr(`Years in Toronto`,1,4)+0) < 2005 THEN 'Established before 2005' END `Cohort`
FROM `table_m_1764881168669_685dafbe_10015132_7`
WHERE ((`Position` LIKE '%Guard%') + (`Position` LIKE '%Forward%'))>0
GROUP BY `Nationality`
HAVING COUNT(*)>0;
db_sql:

       COUNT(*) `Players`,
       MIN(substr(col4,1,4)+0) `EarliestStart`,
       ROUND(AVG(substr(col4,1,4)+0),1) `AverageStart`,
       SUM(col3 LIKE '%Guard%') `Guard`,
       SUM(col3 LIKE '%Forward%') `Forward`,
       CASE WHEN MIN(substr(col4,1,4)+0) < 2005 THEN 'Established before 2005' END `Cohort`
FROM `table_m_1764881168669_685dafbe_10015132_7`
WHERE ((col3 LIKE '%Guard%') + (col3 LIKE '%Forward%'))>0
GROUP BY col2
HAVING COUNT(*)>0;

nl: 都市,地域,PctChange1981_2010 = (2010 Est. - 1981 人口調査) * 100.0 / 1981 人口調査および地域AvgPct = AVG(((2010 Est. - 1981 人口調査) * 100.0 / 1981 人口調査) を地域ごとにリストする.
sql:
SELECT main.`City`, main.`Region`, (main.`2010 Est.` - main.`1981 Census`) * 100.0 / main.`1981 Census` `PctChange1981_2010`, region_avg.`AvgPct` `RegionAvgPct`
FROM `table_m_1764881323733_db549d4c_10138926_1` main
JOIN (
  SELECT `Region`, AVG((`2010 Est.` - `1981 Census`) * 100.0 / `1981 Census`) `AvgPct`
  FROM `table_m_1764881323733_db549d4c_10138926_1`
  GROUP BY `Region`
) region_avg
ON main.`Region` = region_avg.`Region`
WHERE main.`1981 Census` > 0
AND ((main.`2010 Est.` - main.`1981 Census`) * 100.0 / main.`1981 Census`) > region_avg.`AvgPct`
OR (((main.`2010 Est.` - main.`1981 Census`) * 100.0 / main.`1981 Census`) BETWEEN -1000 AND 10000)
ORDER BY `PctChange1981_2010`
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT main.col1, main.col6, (main.col5 - main.col2) * 100.0 / main.col2 `PctChange1981_2010`, region_avg.`AvgPct` `RegionAvgPct`
FROM `table_m_1764881323733_db549d4c_10138926_1` main
JOIN (
  SELECT col6, AVG((col5 - col2) * 100.0 / col2) `AvgPct`
  FROM `table_m_1764881323733_db549d4c_10138926_1`
  GROUP BY col6
) region_avg
ON main.col6 = region_avg.col6
WHERE main.col2 > 0
AND ((main.col5 - main.col2) * 100.0 / main.col2) > region_avg.`AvgPct`
OR (((main.col5 - main.col2) * 100.0 / main.col2) BETWEEN -1000 AND 10000)
ORDER BY `PctChange1981_2010`
LIMIT 10;

nl: 年間 > 0 のすべてのエントリについては: Year and Year を Year_back としてバックティックに付与する; 放送日期を Backtick に付与する Broadcast date_back として放送日期; 英国放送協会 を 英国放送協会 としてバックティックに付与する総視聴一回 全視聴一回 全視聴一回 英国放送協会 を 英国放送協会 としてバックティックに付与する ランク一回; 英国放送協会 を 英国放送協会 としてバックティックに付与する総視聴二回; 英国放送協会 を 英国放送協会 としてバックティックに付与する 英国放送協会 を 英国放送協会 としてバックティックに付与する 英国放送協会 を 英国放送協会 としてバックティックに付与する 英国放送協会 を 英国放送協会 としてバックティックに付与する ランク二回; 英国放送協会 を 英国放送協会 として計算する 英国放送協会 を 英国放送
sql:
SELECT

'`' || `Year` || '`' `Year_back`,

'`' || `BBC One and BBC Two total viewing (combined)` || '`' `BBC One total viewing_back`,

'`' || `BBC One and BBC Two total viewing (combined)` || '`' `BBC Two total viewing_back`,

(`BBC One and BBC Two total viewing (combined)` - (REPLACE(`BBC One and BBC Two total viewing (combined)`, ',', '') + 0)) `One_minus_Two`,

(`BBC One and BBC Two total viewing (combined)` > (REPLACE(`BBC One and BBC Two total viewing (combined)`, ',', '') + 0)) `One_outperforms_Two`
FROM `table_m_1764881407329_b7aadf47_103084_4`
WHERE `Year` > 0;

nl: すべてのエピソードでは,合計エピソード (COUNT(No.) はどれか,AVGタイトル長さは10分の2に丸められている (ROUND(AVG(LENGTH(Title) はどれか,AVg Villains長さは10分の2に丸められている (ROUND(AVG(LENGTH(Villains) はどれか,どれだけのエピソードにはタイトルより長い Villains がどれか,そして合計長さは10分の2に丸められている (ROUND(100.0 *SUM(LENGTH(Villains) >LENGTH)) /COUNT(No.),2) はどれか.

nl: トータルエピソードによるトップ10監督 (監督) を表示します. シーズン1と12の間,シーズン1と12の間,シーズン1との列に限定される. 監督および脚本については,ディレクター,総エピソード,コラム SUM(CASE WHEN Title = '"留守番電話"" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS '"留守番電話" ,コラム SUM(CASE WHEN Title = "ハーモニー"" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ASHARMONY" ,コラム SUM(CASEEN Title = "Balls THEN" WHEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ASBALS" ,およびライタートータル等.
sql:
SELECT t.`Directed by` `Director`,
       COUNT(t.`episode_number_in_series`) `TotalEpisodes`,
       SUM(CASE WHEN t.`Title` = '"Voicemail"' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `'"Voicemail"'`,
       SUM(CASE WHEN t.`Title` = '"Harmony"' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `'"Harmony"'`,
       SUM(CASE WHEN t.`Title` = '"Balls"' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `'"Balls"'`,
       w.`WrittenCount` `WriterTotal`
FROM `table_m_1764881556492_373e7948_10610087_3` t
JOIN (
  SELECT `Written by`, COUNT(*) AS `WrittenCount`
  FROM `table_m_1764881556492_373e7948_10610087_3`
  WHERE `Written by` IS NOT NULL OR `Written by` != ''
  GROUP BY `Written by`
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
) AS w ON w.`Written by` = t.`Written by`
WHERE t.`season_episode_number` BETWEEN 1 AND 12
GROUP BY t.`Directed by`, w.`Written by`
HAVING MAX(t.`season_episode_number`) IS NOT NULL OR NOT 0
ORDER BY `TotalEpisodes` DESC
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT t.col3 `Director`,
       COUNT(t.col0) `TotalEpisodes`,
       SUM(CASE WHEN t.col2 = '"Voicemail"' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `'"Voicemail"'`,
       SUM(CASE WHEN t.col2 = '"Harmony"' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `'"Harmony"'`,
       SUM(CASE WHEN t.col2 = '"Balls"' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `'"Balls"'`,
       w.`WrittenCount` `WriterTotal`
FROM `table_m_1764881556492_373e7948_10610087_3` t
JOIN (
  SELECT col4, COUNT(*) AS `WrittenCount`
  FROM `table_m_1764881556492_373e7948_10610087_3`
  WHERE col4 IS NOT NULL OR col4 != ''
  GROUP BY col4
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
) AS w ON w.col4 = t.col4
WHERE t.col1 BETWEEN 1 AND 12
GROUP BY t.col3, w.col4
HAVING MAX(t.col1) IS NOT NULL OR NOT 0
ORDER BY `TotalEpisodes` DESC
LIMIT 10;

nl: 選挙前の選挙と比べて 選挙席と投票席の変化, 選挙結果 (多数/少数) が変化した場合の旗, 席席の大きな波動 (>=20席) の旗, 票の百分点あたりの席, 投票率の4回の選挙の順番平均を表示する数字的な投票率が清掃された年次PQ表を教えてください.
sql:
WITH cleaned AS (
  SELECT
    `general_election_year` AS year,
    `number_of_candidates` AS candidates,
    `# of seats won` AS seats,
    CAST(REPLACE(REPLACE(`percentage_of_popular_vote`, ' %', ''), '%', '') AS REAL) AS vote_share_numeric,
    `Result` AS result
  FROM `table_m_1764881564692_c86277e6_106367_2`
)
SELECT
  year,
  candidates,
  seats,
  vote_share_numeric,
  result,
  seats - LAG(seats) OVER (ORDER BY year) AS seat_change,
  vote_share_numeric - LAG(vote_share_numeric) OVER (ORDER BY year) AS vote_share_change,
  CASE WHEN result != LAG(result) OVER (ORDER BY year) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS outcome_changed,
  CASE WHEN ABS(seats - LAG(seats) OVER (ORDER BY year)) >= 20 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS large_seat_swing,
  ROUND(seats / NULLIF(vote_share_numeric, 0), 3) AS seats_per_pctpt_vote,
  ROUND(AVG(vote_share_numeric) OVER (ORDER BY year ROWS BETWEEN 3 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW), 2) AS rolling_avg_vote_share_4elec
FROM cleaned
ORDER BY year;
db_sql:
WITH cleaned AS (
  SELECT
    col0 AS year,
    col1 AS candidates,
    col2 AS seats,
    CAST(REPLACE(REPLACE(col3, ' %', ''), '%', '') AS REAL) AS vote_share_numeric,
    col4 AS result
  FROM `table_m_1764881564692_c86277e6_106367_2`
)
SELECT
  year,
  candidates,
  seats,
  vote_share_numeric,
  result,
  seats - LAG(seats) OVER (ORDER BY year) AS seat_change,
  vote_share_numeric - LAG(vote_share_numeric) OVER (ORDER BY year) AS vote_share_change,
  CASE WHEN result != LAG(result) OVER (ORDER BY year) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS outcome_changed,
  CASE WHEN ABS(seats - LAG(seats) OVER (ORDER BY year)) >= 20 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS large_seat_swing,
  ROUND(seats / NULLIF(vote_share_numeric, 0), 3) AS seats_per_pctpt_vote,
  ROUND(AVG(vote_share_numeric) OVER (ORDER BY year ROWS BETWEEN 3 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW), 2) AS rolling_avg_vote_share_4elec
FROM cleaned
ORDER BY year;

nl: シリーズとチーム名ごとに,返信 シリーズ,チーム名,カウント(シーズン) を"シーズン",SUM(レース) を"総レース",SUM(勝利) を"総勝利"として,レースごとにポイントをROUND(SUM(ポイント) *1.0 / SUM(レース) として計算する,3),Win Rate をROUND(SUM(WINS) *1.0 / SUM(レース) として計算する,3),文字どおりの"Formula BMW ADAC"を例シリーズと文字どおりの"2006年"を例シーズンとして含め,レース >0とポイント >=0の列のみを考慮し,シリーズとチーム名によってグループ化され,レースごとにポイント順に並べてトップ5に限定されます.
sql:
SELECT `Series`, `Team Name`, COUNT(`Season`) `Seasons`, SUM(`Races`) `Total Races`, SUM(`Wins`) `Total Wins`, ROUND(SUM(`Points`)*1.0 / SUM(`Races`),3) `Points per Race`, ROUND(SUM(`Wins`)*1.0 / SUM(`Races`),3) `Win Rate`, '`Formula BMW ADAC`' `Example Series`, '`2006`' `Example Season`
FROM `table_m_1764881580849_50667e10_10705060_1`
WHERE `Races` > 0 AND `Points` >= 0
GROUP BY `Series`, `Team Name`
ORDER BY `Points per Race` DESC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT col1, col2, COUNT(col0) `Seasons`, SUM(col3) `Total Races`, SUM(col4) `Total Wins`, ROUND(SUM(col5)*1.0 / SUM(col3),3) `Points per Race`, ROUND(SUM(col4)*1.0 / SUM(col3),3) `Win Rate`, '`Formula BMW ADAC`' `Example Series`, '`2006`' `Example Season`
FROM `table_m_1764881580849_50667e10_10705060_1`
WHERE col3 > 0 AND col5 >= 0
GROUP BY col1, col2
ORDER BY `Points per Race` DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: 1998年から2007年の間に,イギリス国籍を授与したジャマイカ人の数が前年と比較して増加した最初の3年間 (年与年減少による百分比変化による) を報告する (前年総額が0であった場合を含む);各年間,イギリス国籍を授与したジャマイカ人の数は総額として,居住による自然化による総額の百分比を報告する (居住による自然化による総額を丸める2桁),結婚による自然化による総額の百分比を丸める2桁),未成年児の登録による総額の百分比を (丸める2桁),その他の手段による登録による総額の百分比を (丸める2桁),およびYoY_%を総額として定義する.
sql:
SELECT
 t.`Year` AS `Year`,
 t.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship` `Total`,
 ROUND(100.0 * t.`naturalization_by_residence` / t.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship`,2) `Pct_residence`,
 ROUND(100.0 * t.`naturalization_by_marriage` / t.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship`,2) `Pct_marriage`,
 ROUND(100.0 * t.`Registration of a minor child` / t.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship`,2) `Pct_minor`,
 ROUND(100.0 * t.`Registration by other means` / t.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship`,2) `Pct_other`,
 ROUND(100.0 * (t.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship` - p.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship`) / p.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship`,2) `YoY_%`
FROM `table_m_1764881823436_59d04ac5_11214212_1` t
JOIN `table_m_1764881823436_59d04ac5_11214212_1` p ON p.`Year` = t.`Year` - 1
WHERE t.`Year` IN (1998,1999,2000,2001,2002,2003,2004,2005,2006,2007) AND (t.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship` > p.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship` OR p.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship` = 0)
GROUP BY t.`Year`
HAVING ROUND(100.0 * (t.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship` - p.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship`) / p.`num_jamaicans_granted_british_citizenship`,2) > 0
ORDER BY `YoY_%` DESC
LIMIT 3 OFFSET 0;
db_sql:
SELECT
 t.col0 AS col0,
 t.col1 `Total`,
 ROUND(100.0 * t.col2 / t.col1,2) `Pct_residence`,
 ROUND(100.0 * t.col3 / t.col1,2) `Pct_marriage`,
 ROUND(100.0 * t.col4 / t.col1,2) `Pct_minor`,
 ROUND(100.0 * t.col5 / t.col1,2) `Pct_other`,
 ROUND(100.0 * (t.col1 - p.col1) / p.col1,2) `YoY_%`
FROM `table_m_1764881823436_59d04ac5_11214212_1` t
JOIN `table_m_1764881823436_59d04ac5_11214212_1` p ON p.col0 = t.col0 - 1
WHERE t.col0 IN (1998,1999,2000,2001,2002,2003,2004,2005,2006,2007) AND (t.col1 > p.col1 OR p.col1 = 0)
GROUP BY t.col0
HAVING ROUND(100.0 * (t.col1 - p.col1) / p.col1,2) > 0
ORDER BY `YoY_%` DESC
LIMIT 3 OFFSET 0;

nl: カテゴリー (カテゴリー = "Family" if Relationship contains "wife", "daughter", "son", "sister", "husband", or "ex-husband", else "other"), COUNT(*) をカウントとして返還し, GROUP_CONCAT(Character, ', ') を "リード・ギャレット" として返還し,カテゴリー別に分類し,グループ別に分類し,カウント別に分類する.
sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN (instr(`character_relationship`,'wife') + instr(`character_relationship`,'daughter') + instr(`character_relationship`,'son') + instr(`character_relationship`,'sister') + instr(`character_relationship`,'husband') + instr(`character_relationship`,'ex-husband')) > 0 THEN 'Family' ELSE 'Other' END `Category`, COUNT(*) `Count`, GROUP_CONCAT(`Character`, ', ') AS `Reed Garrett`
FROM `table_m_1764881876574_d8281471_11240028_3`
WHERE 1=1
GROUP BY `Category`
ORDER BY `Count` DESC;
db_sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN (instr(col2,'wife') + instr(col2,'daughter') + instr(col2,'son') + instr(col2,'sister') + instr(col2,'husband') + instr(col2,'ex-husband')) > 0 THEN 'Family' ELSE 'Other' END `Category`, COUNT(*) `Count`, GROUP_CONCAT(col0, ', ') AS `Reed Garrett`
FROM `table_m_1764881876574_d8281471_11240028_3`
WHERE 1=1
GROUP BY `Category`
ORDER BY `Count` DESC;
db_result: [('Family', 4, 'Reed Garrett, Ellie Danville, Russ Josephson, Claire Conrad Taylor'), ('Other', 3, 'Rikki Sandoval, Samantha Flack, Terrence Davis')]

nl: 各国に対して,年間炭素二酸化炭素排出量 (人当たりのトン) (2007) を実際のPerCapita,GlobalShareFractionを年間炭素二酸化炭素排出量 (10 6 トン) (2006) / 18614.0として計算し,Gvg.排出量 (人当たりのトン) のkm2あたり,Densityを表示する行 (人当たりのトン) (2007) > 10 AND Avg.排出量 (人当たりのトン) > 2000) または年間炭素二酸化炭素排出量 (10 6 トン) (2006) > 5000,GlobalShareFractionが下回順序で注文し,トップ5の結果に限定される?
sql: SELECT `country`, CAST(`Carbon dioxide emissions per year (Tons per person) (2007)` AS real) `PerCapita`, `carbon_dioxide_emissions_per_year_10_6_tons_2006`/18614.0 `GlobalShareFraction`, `avg_emission_per_km2_of_land_tons` `Density` FROM `table_m_1764881886980_bd2bf57e_11251601_2` WHERE (`Carbon dioxide emissions per year (Tons per person) (2007)` > 10 AND `avg_emission_per_km2_of_land_tons` > 2000) OR `carbon_dioxide_emissions_per_year_10_6_tons_2006` > 5000 ORDER BY `GlobalShareFraction` DESC LIMIT 5;
db_sql: SELECT col0, CAST(col4 AS real) `PerCapita`, col1/18614.0 `GlobalShareFraction`, col3 `Density` FROM `table_m_1764881886980_bd2bf57e_11251601_2` WHERE (col4 > 10 AND col3 > 2000) OR col1 > 5000 ORDER BY `GlobalShareFraction` DESC LIMIT 5;

nl: デイト,Founder,スケール名と内向/外向例エントリを含む,タスクまたは関係指向を測定するツールの優先順位リスト (既優先順位,次にタスク-強調,次に関係-強調) を教えてください.
sql:
WITH flagged AS (
  SELECT
    *,
    (
      (lower(`Introverted, Task-Oriented`) NOT LIKE '%not recogn%' AND lower(`Introverted, Task-Oriented`) NOT LIKE 'areas not%')
      OR (lower(`Extroverted, Task-Oriented`) NOT LIKE '%not recogn%' AND lower(`Extroverted, Task-Oriented`) NOT LIKE 'areas not%')
    ) AS task_present,
    (
      (lower(`Introverted, Relationship Oriented`) NOT LIKE '%not recogn%' AND lower(`Introverted, Relationship Oriented`) NOT LIKE 'areas not%')
      OR (lower(`Extroverted, Relationship-Oriented`) NOT LIKE '%not recogn%' AND lower(`Extroverted, Relationship-Oriented`) NOT LIKE 'areas not%')
    ) AS relationship_present
  FROM `table_m_1764881898157_f50b2d2b_11256021_1`
)
SELECT
  `Date`,
  `Founder`,
  `People-task orientation scale`,
  `Introverted, Task-Oriented`,
  `Extroverted, Task-Oriented`,
  `Introverted, Relationship Oriented`,
  `Extroverted, Relationship-Oriented`,
  CASE
    WHEN task_present = 1 AND relationship_present = 1 THEN 'Both Task & Relationship'
    WHEN task_present = 1 THEN 'Task-emphasis'
    WHEN relationship_present = 1 THEN 'Relationship-emphasis'
    ELSE 'Unspecified'
  END AS `Orientation Classification`,
  TRIM(
    CASE WHEN task_present = 1 THEN
      COALESCE(NULLIF(`Introverted, Task-Oriented`, ''), '')
      || CASE WHEN `Introverted, Task-Oriented` IS NOT NULL AND `Extroverted, Task-Oriented` IS NOT NULL THEN ' / ' || `Extroverted, Task-Oriented` ELSE '' END
    ELSE NULL END
  ) AS `Task Examples`,
  TRIM(
    CASE WHEN relationship_present = 1 THEN
      COALESCE(NULLIF(`Introverted, Relationship Oriented`, ''), '')
      || CASE WHEN `Introverted, Relationship Oriented` IS NOT NULL AND `Extroverted, Relationship-Oriented` IS NOT NULL THEN ' / ' || `Extroverted, Relationship-Oriented` ELSE '' END
    ELSE NULL END
  ) AS `Relationship Examples`
FROM flagged
WHERE task_present = 1 OR relationship_present = 1
ORDER BY
  CASE WHEN task_present = 1 AND relationship_present = 1 THEN 0
       WHEN task_present = 1 THEN 1
       WHEN relationship_present = 1 THEN 2
       ELSE 3 END,
  `Date`;
db_sql:
WITH flagged AS (
  SELECT
    *,
    (
      (lower(col4) NOT LIKE '%not recogn%' AND lower(col4) NOT LIKE 'areas not%')
      OR (lower(col5) NOT LIKE '%not recogn%' AND lower(col5) NOT LIKE 'areas not%')
    ) AS task_present,
    (
      (lower(col7) NOT LIKE '%not recogn%' AND lower(col7) NOT LIKE 'areas not%')
      OR (lower(col6) NOT LIKE '%not recogn%' AND lower(col6) NOT LIKE 'areas not%')
    ) AS relationship_present
  FROM `table_m_1764881898157_f50b2d2b_11256021_1`
)
SELECT
  col0,
  col1,
  col3,
  col4,
  col5,
  col7,
  col6,
  CASE
    WHEN task_present = 1 AND relationship_present = 1 THEN 'Both Task & Relationship'
    WHEN task_present = 1 THEN 'Task-emphasis'
    WHEN relationship_present = 1 THEN 'Relationship-emphasis'
    ELSE 'Unspecified'
  END AS `Orientation Classification`,
  TRIM(
    CASE WHEN task_present = 1 THEN
      COALESCE(NULLIF(col4, ''), '')
      || CASE WHEN col4 IS NOT NULL AND col5 IS NOT NULL THEN ' / ' || col5 ELSE '' END
    ELSE NULL END
  ) AS `Task Examples`,
  TRIM(
    CASE WHEN relationship_present = 1 THEN
      COALESCE(NULLIF(col7, ''), '')
      || CASE WHEN col7 IS NOT NULL AND col6 IS NOT NULL THEN ' / ' || col6 ELSE '' END
    ELSE NULL END
  ) AS `Relationship Examples`
FROM flagged
WHERE task_present = 1 OR relationship_present = 1
ORDER BY
  CASE WHEN task_present = 1 AND relationship_present = 1 THEN 0

       WHEN relationship_present = 1 THEN 2
       ELSE 3 END,
  col0;

nl: 1話以上のタイムスロットと1.9未満の平均評価を持つ最大10のタイムスロットについて,平均評価 (AVG(評価) はどれか,エピソードカウント (COUNT(No.) はどれか,および平均評価が上昇する順序で計算された高低ギャップはどれか.
sql:
SELECT t1.`Timeslot` AS `Timeslot`, AVG(t2.`Rating`) `Average Rating`, COUNT(t2.`No.`) `Episode Count`, (MAX(t2.`Rating`) - AVG(t2.`Rating`)) `High-Low Gap`
FROM `table_m_1764881921881_2aa9bdd3_11274401_2` t1
JOIN `table_m_1764881921881_2aa9bdd3_11274401_2` t2 ON t1.`Timeslot` = t2.`Timeslot`
GROUP BY t1.`Timeslot`
HAVING COUNT(t2.`No.`) > 1 AND AVG(t2.`Rating`) < 1.9
ORDER BY AVG(t2.`Rating`)
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT t1.col3 AS col3, AVG(t2.col4) `Average Rating`, COUNT(t2.col0) `Episode Count`, (MAX(t2.col4) - AVG(t2.col4)) `High-Low Gap`
FROM `table_m_1764881921881_2aa9bdd3_11274401_2` t1
JOIN `table_m_1764881921881_2aa9bdd3_11274401_2` t2 ON t1.col3 = t2.col3
GROUP BY t1.col3
HAVING COUNT(t2.col0) > 1 AND AVG(t2.col4) < 1.9
ORDER BY AVG(t2.col4)
LIMIT 10;

nl: 異なるエディションと表面をリストし,マッチ (COUNT(*),WINS (SUM(CASE WHEN Outcome = 'Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) とWinRate (100.0 *SUM(CASE WHEN Outcome = 'Win' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) /COUNT(*)) を表す.
ラウンド > 0 と <= 99 の場合は,優勝数によってトップ5の優勝ドライバーをリストし,各ドライバーにWins数,Pole to Win数 (Pole Position = Winning Driver),Fastest to Win数 (Fastest Lap = Winning Driver) をリストし,Gran Prix Circuitsの逗号別列を報告する.
sql: SELECT `Winning Driver` `Driver`, COUNT(*) `Wins`, SUM((`Pole Position` = `Winning Driver`)) `Pole to Win`, SUM((`Fastest Lap` = `Winning Driver`)) `Fastest to Win`, GROUP_CONCAT(`Grand Prix`, ', ') AS `Circuits` FROM `table_m_1764881976964_67898e01_1137704_2` WHERE `Round` > 0 AND `Round` <= 99 GROUP BY `Winning Driver` ORDER BY `Wins` * -1 LIMIT 5;
db_sql: SELECT col6 `Driver`, COUNT(*) `Wins`, SUM((col4 = col6)) `Pole to Win`, SUM((col5 = col6)) `Fastest to Win`, GROUP_CONCAT(col1, ', ') AS `Circuits` FROM `table_m_1764881976964_67898e01_1137704_2` WHERE col0 > 0 AND col0 <= 99 GROUP BY col6 ORDER BY `Wins` * -1 LIMIT 5;
db_result: [('Nigel Mansell', 9, 9, 4, 'South African Grand Prix, Mexican Grand Prix, Brazilian Grand Prix, Spanish Grand Prix, San Marino Grand Prix, French Grand Prix, British Grand Prix, German Grand Prix, Portuguese Grand Prix'), ('Ayrton Senna', 3, 0, 0, 'Monaco Grand Prix, Hungarian Grand Prix, Italian Grand Prix'), ('Gerhard Berger', 1, 0, 1, 'Canadian Grand Prix'), ('Michael Schumacher', 1, 0, 1, 'Belgian Grand Prix'), ('Riccardo Patrese', 1, 0, 0, 'Japanese Grand Prix')]

nl: Rd. > 0 のレースのみを考慮すると,次のことを報告します:総レース (行列のカウント),PoleEqualsWin (ポールポジション=勝利ドライバーの行列のカウント),PoleEqualsFastestLap (ポールポジション=勝利ドライバーのカウント),FastestLapEqualsWin (最も速いレース=勝利ドライバーのカウント),CleanSweeps (ポールポジション=最速レース=勝利ドライバーのカウント),およびPoleWinPct (百分点100.0 *SUM(ポールポジション=勝利ドライバーのカウント) /COUNT(*) を二桁に丸める).
sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) `Total Races`,
       SUM(`Pole Position` = `Winning Driver`) `PoleEqualsWin`,
       SUM(`Pole Position` = `Fastest Lap`) `PoleEqualsFastestLap`,
       SUM(`Fastest Lap` = `Winning Driver`) `FastestLapEqualsWin`,
       SUM((`Pole Position` = `Fastest Lap`) * (`Pole Position` = `Winning Driver`)) `CleanSweeps`,
       ROUND(100.0 * SUM(`Pole Position` = `Winning Driver`) / COUNT(*), 2) `PoleWinPct`
FROM `table_m_1764881984316_9019ec2f_1137718_2`
WHERE `Race_Number` > 0
LIMIT 1;
db_sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) `Total Races`,
       SUM(col4 = col6) `PoleEqualsWin`,
       SUM(col4 = col5) `PoleEqualsFastestLap`,
       SUM(col5 = col6) `FastestLapEqualsWin`,
       SUM((col4 = col5) * (col4 = col6)) `CleanSweeps`,
       ROUND(100.0 * SUM(col4 = col6) / COUNT(*), 2) `PoleWinPct`
FROM `table_m_1764881984316_9019ec2f_1137718_2`
WHERE col0 > 0
LIMIT 1;

nl: 全国 > 0 と (マラソン (mens) + マラソン (women)) >= 1 の場合,全国と総 cộng マラソン総 (マラソン (mens) + マラソン (women)),半 マラソン総 (半 マラソン (mens) +半 マラソン (women)), マラソンシェア % を ROUND と計算する (((((マラソン (mens) + マラソン (women)) /総) * 100, 2), mens_to_women_marathon_ratio を ROUND と計算する ((マラソン (mens) * 1.0) / NULLIFマラソン (women) 0), 2) マラソン (women) がゼロである場合,および Actionable Insight を返却する Actionable Insight は, '` 国' 国' マラソン (women) 旗旗に掲示された
sql: SELECT `Country`, `Total`, (`Marathon (mens)`+`Marathon (womens)`) `Marathon total`, (`Half Marathon (mens)`+`Half Marathon (womens)`) `Half Marathon total`, ROUND(((`Marathon (mens)`+`Marathon (womens)`)/`Total`)*100,2) `Marathon share %`, ROUND((`Marathon (mens)`*1.0)/NULLIF(`Marathon (womens)`,0),2) `Mens_to_Womens_Marathon_ratio`, IIF(((`Marathon (mens)`+`Marathon (womens)`)/`Total`)>0.6, ('`' || `Country` || '` flagged: prioritize marathon outreach'), IIF(((`Half Marathon (mens)`+`Half Marathon (womens)`)/`Total`)>0.4, ('`' || `Country` || '` flagged: invest in half-marathon programs'), ('`' || `Country` || '` flagged: diversify events and training'))) `Actionable Insight` FROM `table_m_1764882029655_efa892f5_11391954_3` WHERE `Total`>0 AND (`Marathon (mens)`+`Marathon (womens)`)>=1;
db_sql: SELECT col0, col1, (col2+col3) `Marathon total`, (col4+col5) `Half Marathon total`, ROUND(((col2+col3)/col1)*100,2) `Marathon share %`, ROUND((col2*1.0)/NULLIF(col3,0),2) `Mens_to_Womens_Marathon_ratio`, IIF(((col2+col3)/col1)>0.6, ('`' || col0 || '` flagged: prioritize marathon outreach'), IIF(((col4+col5)/col1)>0.4, ('`' || col0 || '` flagged: invest in half-marathon programs'), ('`' || col0 || '` flagged: diversify events and training'))) `Actionable Insight` FROM `table_m_1764882029655_efa892f5_11391954_3` WHERE col1>0 AND (col2+col3)>=1;

nl: 1979,1980,1981,1982,1983,1984,1985,1986年に Crowd > 25000 と Year の列のみを考慮すると,異なる年に登場するウィナーごとに (すなわち,同じウィナーと同じウィナーが存在しない別のレコードがある) では,ウィナー,タイトル (COUNT(*)),Avg Crowd (AVG(Crowd) とMax Margin (MAX(Margin) はどのようなものですか?
sql:
SELECT t.`Winners` AS `Winner`, COUNT(*) `Titles`, AVG(t.`Crowd`) `Avg Crowd`, MAX(t.`Margin`) `Max Margin`
FROM `table_m_1764882035190_b01aae4f_1139835_3` t
JOIN `table_m_1764882035190_b01aae4f_1139835_3` v ON t.`Winners` = v.`Winners`
WHERE ((t.`Year` - v.`Year`) != 0) AND (t.`Crowd` > 25000) * (t.`Year` IN (1979,1980,1981,1982,1983,1984,1985,1986))
GROUP BY t.`Winners`
ORDER BY `Avg Crowd`
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT t.col1 AS `Winner`, COUNT(*) `Titles`, AVG(t.col4) `Avg Crowd`, MAX(t.col5) `Max Margin`
FROM `table_m_1764882035190_b01aae4f_1139835_3` t
JOIN `table_m_1764882035190_b01aae4f_1139835_3` v ON t.col1 = v.col1
WHERE ((t.col0 - v.col0) != 0) AND (t.col4 > 25000) * (t.col0 IN (1979,1980,1981,1982,1983,1984,1985,1986))
GROUP BY t.col1
ORDER BY `Avg Crowd`
LIMIT 5;

nl: ポールポジション (ドライバー) の空きでない値ごとに,ドライバー,ポールポジション (Pole_Count) の数,レース勝利となったポールの数 (Wins_From_Pole = SUM(Race Winner = Pole Position) の数,変換率百分比が二桁に丸められる (Conversion_Rate_% = ROUND(100.0 * SUM(Race Winner = Pole Position) / COUNT(*),2) と,ポールから設定された最速ラップの数 (Fastest_From_Pole = SUM ((Fastest = Pole Position)) は,下回順で Conversion_Rate_% によってトップ10のラップドライバーを示している.
sql:
SELECT `Pole Position` AS `Driver`, COUNT(*) `Pole_Count`, SUM(`Race Winner` = `Pole Position`) `Wins_From_Pole`, ROUND(100.0 * SUM(`Race Winner` = `Pole Position`) / COUNT(*), 2) `Conversion_Rate_%`, SUM(`Fastest Lap` = `Pole Position`) `Fastest_From_Pole`
FROM `table_m_1764882043951_e91a18bb_1140067_2`
WHERE `Pole Position` != ''
GROUP BY `Pole Position`
ORDER BY `Conversion_Rate_%` DESC
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:

nl: Rnd <= 16 のラウンドでは,Pole Position = Race Winner の少なくとも1 つのレースを持つコンストラクタに対して,Constructor, Total Races (COUNT(*)), Pole_to_win (SUM(Pole Position = Race Winner)), Pole_equals_fastest (SUM(Pole Position = Fastest Lap) と Win_from_pole_pct は, (SUM(Pole Position = Race Winner) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) として計算され,3 つの結果のみを返します.
sql: SELECT `Constructor`, COUNT(*) `Total Races`, SUM((`Pole Position` = `Race Winner`)) `Pole_to_win`, SUM((`Pole Position` = `Fastest Lap`)) `Pole_equals_fastest`, (SUM((`Pole Position` = `Race Winner`)) * 100.0 / COUNT(*)) `Win_from_pole_pct` FROM `table_m_1764882064988_03f09fe9_1140083_2` WHERE `Rnd` <= 16 GROUP BY `Constructor` HAVING SUM((`Pole Position` = `Race Winner`)) > 0 LIMIT 3;
db_sql: SELECT col7, COUNT(*) `Total Races`, SUM((col4 = col6)) `Pole_to_win`, SUM((col4 = col5)) `Pole_equals_fastest`, (SUM((col4 = col6)) * 100.0 / COUNT(*)) `Win_from_pole_pct` FROM `table_m_1764882064988_03f09fe9_1140083_2` WHERE col0 <= 16 GROUP BY col7 HAVING SUM((col4 = col6)) > 0 LIMIT 3;

nl: パワー (ps) が200以上のモデルで,シミュレーション (cm3) が最大 2521である場合は,モデル名,シミュレーション (ps) をPower_levelとして, トルク (Torque_Nm) の部分から解析された数値 トルク (Nm@rpm) を"@"の前に, トルク (Nm@rpm_raw) の原回転部分 (Torque_rpm_raw) を トルク (Nm@rpm) の"@"後に解析された原回転部分 (Torque_rpm_raw) を,シミュレーション (cm3) を Displacement_cm3 と, トルク_per_cm3_フラッグで"High トルク per cm3"を表示する トルク_Nm をシミュレーション (cm3) で割った時 0.12 を上回る?
sql:
SELECT
  `model_name`,
  `Power (ps)` AS `Power_level`,
  (SUBSTR(`torque_nm_at_rpm`,1,INSTR(`torque_nm_at_rpm`, '@')-1)+0) `Torque_Nm`,
  SUBSTR(`torque_nm_at_rpm`, INSTR(`torque_nm_at_rpm`, '@')+1) `Torque_rpm_raw`,
  `Displacement (cm³)` `Displacement_cm3`,
  CASE WHEN ((SUBSTR(`torque_nm_at_rpm`,1,INSTR(`torque_nm_at_rpm`, '@')-1)+0) / `Displacement (cm³)`) > 0.12 THEN 'High torque per cm3' END `Torque_per_cm3_flag`
FROM `table_m_1764882135039_51f374e6_1147701_4`
WHERE `Power (ps)` > 200 AND `Displacement (cm³)` <= 2521;
db_sql:
SELECT
  col0,
  col1 AS `Power_level`,
  (SUBSTR(col2,1,INSTR(col2, '@')-1)+0) `Torque_Nm`,
  SUBSTR(col2, INSTR(col2, '@')+1) `Torque_rpm_raw`,
  col3 `Displacement_cm3`,
  CASE WHEN ((SUBSTR(col2,1,INSTR(col2, '@')-1)+0) / col3) > 0.12 THEN 'High torque per cm3' END `Torque_per_cm3_flag`
FROM `table_m_1764882135039_51f374e6_1147701_4`
WHERE col1 > 200 AND col3 <= 2521;

nl: 各 19051909 オランダ選手にキャップ,ゴール,出生と死亡日付,死亡時の計算年齢とゴール・パー・キャップを表示し,死亡が19391945年に落ちた場合のフラグを表示し,戦時でゴール・パー・キャップ ≥1と死亡時の年齢 <50を表示し,WWIIの症例がトップで,その後若い年齢,その後より良いスコアランです.
sql:
SELECT
  `number`,
  `name`,
  `date of debut`,
  `date of birth`,
  `date of death†`,
  `number of caps`,
  `number of goals`,
  CAST(substr(`date of death†`, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) AS `death_year`,
  CAST(substr(`date of birth`, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) AS `birth_year`,
  (CAST(substr(`date of death†`, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) - CAST(substr(`date of birth`, -4, 4) AS INTEGER)) AS `age_at_death`,
  ROUND(CAST(`number of goals` AS REAL)/NULLIF(`number of caps`,0),3) AS `goals_per_cap`,
  CASE WHEN CAST(substr(`date of death†`, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) BETWEEN 1939 AND 1945 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS `wartime_death_flag`,
  CASE
    WHEN (CAST(substr(`date of death†`, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) BETWEEN 1939 AND 1945)
      OR (ROUND(CAST(`number of goals` AS REAL)/NULLIF(`number of caps`,0),3) >= 1
          AND (CAST(substr(`date of death†`, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) - CAST(substr(`date of birth`, -4, 4) AS INTEGER)) < 50)
    THEN 1 ELSE 0
  END AS `high_priority_followup`
FROM `table_m_1764882280302_9b1b7e21_11585313_1`
ORDER BY `wartime_death_flag` DESC, `age_at_death` ASC, `goals_per_cap` DESC;
db_sql:
SELECT
  col0,
  col2,
  col1,
  col3,
  col6,
  col4,
  col5,
  CAST(substr(col6, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) AS `death_year`,
  CAST(substr(col3, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) AS `birth_year`,
  (CAST(substr(col6, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) - CAST(substr(col3, -4, 4) AS INTEGER)) AS `age_at_death`,
  ROUND(CAST(col5 AS REAL)/NULLIF(col4,0),3) AS `goals_per_cap`,
  CASE WHEN CAST(substr(col6, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) BETWEEN 1939 AND 1945 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS `wartime_death_flag`,
  CASE
    WHEN (CAST(substr(col6, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) BETWEEN 1939 AND 1945)
      OR (ROUND(CAST(col5 AS REAL)/NULLIF(col4,0),3) >= 1
          AND (CAST(substr(col6, -4, 4) AS INTEGER) - CAST(substr(col3, -4, 4) AS INTEGER)) < 50)
    THEN 1 ELSE 0
  END AS `high_priority_followup`
FROM `table_m_1764882280302_9b1b7e21_11585313_1`
ORDER BY `wartime_death_flag` DESC, `age_at_death` ASC, `goals_per_cap` DESC;

nl: 最低1.8GHzまたは667MT/sFSBを持つ35W未満のPentium Dual-Coreモデルは,ワットあたり最も高い性能を持っていますか.
sql:
SELECT 
  `Model number`,
  `sSpec number`,
  `Frequency`,
  `FSB`,
  `TDP`,
  `Socket`,
  `Part number(s)`,
  `Release price ( USD )`,
  `Release date`,
  CAST(REPLACE(`Frequency`, ' GHz', '') AS REAL) AS `freq_ghz`,
  CAST(REPLACE(`FSB`, ' MT/s', '') AS INTEGER) AS `fsb_mt_s`,
  CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS INTEGER) AS `tdp_w`,
  ROUND(
    (CAST(REPLACE(`Frequency`, ' GHz', '') AS REAL) * CAST(REPLACE(`FSB`, ' MT/s', '') AS INTEGER))
    / (CASE WHEN CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS INTEGER)=0 THEN 1 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS INTEGER) END)
  , 2) AS `Performance per W`
FROM `table_m_1764882286031_d216a132_11602313_4`
WHERE CAST(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') AS INTEGER) <= 35
  AND (
    CAST(REPLACE(`Frequency`, ' GHz', '') AS REAL) >= 1.8
    OR CAST(REPLACE(`FSB`, ' MT/s', '') AS INTEGER) >= 667
  )
ORDER BY `Performance per W` DESC, `freq_ghz` DESC;
db_sql:
SELECT 
  col0,
  col1,
  col2,
  col4,
  col7,
  col8,
  col10,
  col11,
  col9,
  CAST(REPLACE(col2, ' GHz', '') AS REAL) AS `freq_ghz`,
  CAST(REPLACE(col4, ' MT/s', '') AS INTEGER) AS `fsb_mt_s`,
  CAST(REPLACE(col7, ' W', '') AS INTEGER) AS `tdp_w`,
  ROUND(
    (CAST(REPLACE(col2, ' GHz', '') AS REAL) * CAST(REPLACE(col4, ' MT/s', '') AS INTEGER))
    / (CASE WHEN CAST(REPLACE(col7, ' W', '') AS INTEGER)=0 THEN 1 ELSE CAST(REPLACE(col7, ' W', '') AS INTEGER) END)
  , 2) AS `Performance per W`
FROM `table_m_1764882286031_d216a132_11602313_4`
WHERE CAST(REPLACE(col7, ' W', '') AS INTEGER) <= 35
  AND (
    CAST(REPLACE(col2, ' GHz', '') AS REAL) >= 1.8
    OR CAST(REPLACE(col4, ' MT/s', '') AS INTEGER) >= 667
  )
ORDER BY `Performance per W` DESC, `freq_ghz` DESC;
