nl: エピソード > 260 と セグメント A の最初の単語 (最初のスペースまでの子文字列,またはスペースがない場合 セグメント A 全体) が別のエピソード (すなわち,エピソード値が同じではない) で セグメント B の最初の単語 (最初のスペースまでの子文字列,またはスペースがない場合 セグメント B 全体) に等しい場合のエピソードに異なるエピソード (エピソード値が同じでない場合) のエピソードPair (上昇順に並べて 5 に制限される) として異なるエピソード値を提供してください.
sql:
SELECT DISTINCT t1.`Episode` AS `EpisodePair`
FROM `table_m_1764886189810_983b89e3_15187735_21` t1 JOIN `table_m_1764886189810_983b89e3_15187735_21` t2 ON
substr(t1.`Segment A`,1,IIF(instr(t1.`Segment A`,' ')=0,length(t1.`Segment A`),instr(t1.`Segment A`,' ')-1))
=
substr(t2.`Segment B`,1,IIF(instr(t2.`Segment B`,' ')=0,length(t2.`Segment B`),instr(t2.`Segment B`,' ')-1))
WHERE t1.`Episode` != t2.`Episode` AND t1.`Episode` > 260
ORDER BY `EpisodePair`
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT t1.col1 AS `EpisodePair`
FROM `table_m_1764886189810_983b89e3_15187735_21` t1 JOIN `table_m_1764886189810_983b89e3_15187735_21` t2 ON
substr(t1.col2,1,IIF(instr(t1.col2,' ')=0,length(t1.col2),instr(t1.col2,' ')-1))
=
substr(t2.col3,1,IIF(instr(t2.col3,' ')=0,length(t2.col3),instr(t2.col3,' ')-1))
WHERE t1.col1 != t2.col1 AND t1.col1 > 260
ORDER BY `EpisodePair`
LIMIT 5;

nl: 食品/有機部門と産業/化学部門 (エピソードコード,Netflix IDを表示し,どの部門が食品と産業部門なのか) を組み合わせて シーズン3のエピソードを列挙し,それぞれのエピソードメタデータと列挙します.
sql:
SELECT
  'paired_episode' AS `row_type`,
  `Series Ep.`,
  `Episode`,
  `Netflix`,
  (
    (CASE WHEN `Segment A` IN ('Cranberries','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Dog and Cat Food','Prepared Mustard','Tofu','Couscous','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Fresh Cut Flowers','Hard Candies') THEN '`' || `Segment A` || '`' || ', ' ELSE '' END)
  || (CASE WHEN `Segment B` IN ('Cranberries','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Dog and Cat Food','Prepared Mustard','Tofu','Couscous','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Fresh Cut Flowers','Hard Candies') THEN '`' || `Segment B` || '`' || ', ' ELSE '' END)
  || (CASE WHEN `Segment C` IN ('Cranberries','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Dog and Cat Food','Prepared Mustard','Tofu','Couscous','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Fresh Cut Flowers','Hard Candies') THEN '`' || `Segment C` || '`' || ', ' ELSE '' END)
  || (CASE WHEN `Segment D` IN ('Cranberries','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Dog and Cat Food','Prepared Mustard','Tofu','Couscous','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Fresh Cut Flowers','Hard Candies') THEN '`' || `Segment D` || '`' || ', ' ELSE '' END)
  ) AS `Food_Segments`,
  (
    (CASE WHEN `Segment A` IN ('Asphalt Shingles','Expanded Polystyrene Products','Neon Signs','Adhesive Tape','PVC Gloves','Thermo-formed Glass','Temporary Metal Fences','Combination Locks','Wheel Loaders','Car Radiators','Electric Baseboard Heaters','Inflatable Watercraft','Wind Generators','ed Mould Pulp Containers') THEN '`' || `Segment A` || '`' || ', ' ELSE '' END)
  || (CASE WHEN `Segment B` IN ('Asphalt Shingles','Expanded Polystyrene Products','Neon Signs','Adhesive Tape','PVC Gloves','Thermo-formed Glass','Temporary Metal Fences','Combination Locks','Wheel Loaders','Car Radiators','Electric Baseboard Heaters','Inflatable Watercraft','Wind Generators','ed Mould Pulp Containers') THEN '`' || `Segment B` || '`' || ', ' ELSE '' END)
  || (CASE WHEN `Segment C` IN ('Asphalt Shingles','Expanded Polystyrene Products','Neon Signs','Adhesive Tape','PVC Gloves','Thermo-formed Glass','Temporary Metal Fences','Combination Locks','Wheel Loaders','Car Radiators','Electric Baseboard Heaters','Inflatable Watercraft','Wind Generators','ed Mould Pulp Containers') THEN '`' || `Segment C` || '`' || ', ' ELSE '' END)
  || (CASE WHEN `Segment D` IN ('Asphalt Shingles','Expanded Polystyrene Products','Neon Signs','Adhesive Tape','PVC Gloves','Thermo-formed Glass','Temporary Metal Fences','Combination Locks','Wheel Loaders','Car Radiators','Electric Baseboard Heaters','Inflatable Watercraft','Wind Generators','ed Mould Pulp Containers') THEN '`' || `Segment D` || '`' || ', ' ELSE '' END)
  ) AS `Industrial_Segments`,
  (CASE WHEN (
       `Segment A` IN ('Candles','Asphalt Shingles','Fresh Cut Flowers','Neon Signs','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Tofu','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Hard Candies')
    OR `Segment B` IN ('Candles','Asphalt Shingles','Fresh Cut Flowers','Neon Signs','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Tofu','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Hard Candies')
    OR `Segment C` IN ('Candles','Asphalt Shingles','Fresh Cut Flowers','Neon Signs','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Tofu','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Hard Candies')
    OR `Segment D` IN ('Candles','Asphalt Shingles','Fresh Cut Flowers','Neon Signs','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Tofu','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Hard Candies')
  ) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `Distinctive_Flag`
FROM `table_m_1764886194832_55e90110_15187735_3`
WHERE (
      `Segment A` IN ('Cranberries','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Dog and Cat Food','Prepared Mustard','Tofu','Couscous','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Fresh Cut Flowers','Hard Candies')
   OR `Segment B` IN ('Cranberries','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Dog and Cat Food','Prepared Mustard','Tofu','Couscous','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Fresh Cut Flowers','Hard Candies')
   OR `Segment C` IN ('Cranberries','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Dog and Cat Food','Prepared Mustard','Tofu','Couscous','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Fresh Cut Flowers','Hard Candies')
   OR `Segment D` IN ('Cranberries','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Dog and Cat Food','Prepared Mustard','Tofu','Couscous','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Fresh Cut Flowers','Hard Candies')
)
AND (
      `Segment A` IN ('Asphalt Shingles','Expanded Polystyrene Products','Neon Signs','Adhesive Tape','PVC Gloves','Thermo-formed Glass','Temporary Metal Fences','Combination Locks','Wheel Loaders','Car Radiators','Electric Baseboard Heaters','Inflatable Watercraft','Wind Generators','ed Mould Pulp Containers')
   OR `Segment B` IN ('Asphalt Shingles','Expanded Polystyrene Products','Neon Signs','Adhesive Tape','PVC Gloves','Thermo-formed Glass','Temporary Metal Fences','Combination Locks','Wheel Loaders','Car Radiators','Electric Baseboard Heaters','Inflatable Watercraft','Wind Generators','ed Mould Pulp Containers')
   OR `Segment C` IN ('Asphalt Shingles','Expanded Polystyrene Products','Neon Signs','Adhesive Tape','PVC Gloves','Thermo-formed Glass','Temporary Metal Fences','Combination Locks','Wheel Loaders','Car Radiators','Electric Baseboard Heaters','Inflatable Watercraft','Wind Generators','ed Mould Pulp Containers')
   OR `Segment D` IN ('Asphalt Shingles','Expanded Polystyrene Products','Neon Signs','Adhesive Tape','PVC Gloves','Thermo-formed Glass','Temporary Metal Fences','Combination Locks','Wheel Loaders','Car Radiators','Electric Baseboard Heaters','Inflatable Watercraft','Wind Generators','ed Mould Pulp Containers')
)
UNION ALL
SELECT
  'distinctive_segment' AS `row_type`,
  `Series Ep.`,
  `Episode`,
  `Netflix`,
  '`' || `segment` || '`' AS `Food_Segments`,
  NULL AS `Industrial_Segments`,
  NULL AS `Distinctive_Flag`
FROM (
  SELECT `Series Ep.`, `Episode`, `Netflix`, `Segment A` AS `segment` FROM `table_m_1764886194832_55e90110_15187735_3`
  UNION ALL SELECT `Series Ep.`, `Episode`, `Netflix`, `Segment B` FROM `table_m_1764886194832_55e90110_15187735_3`
  UNION ALL SELECT `Series Ep.`, `Episode`, `Netflix`, `Segment C` FROM `table_m_1764886194832_55e90110_15187735_3`
  UNION ALL SELECT `Series Ep.`, `Episode`, `Netflix`, `Segment D` FROM `table_m_1764886194832_55e90110_15187735_3`
) AS `all_segments`
WHERE `segment` IN ('Candles','Asphalt Shingles','Fresh Cut Flowers','Neon Signs','Vegetable Oil','Yogurt','Tofu','Phyllo Dough','Chicken','Hard Candies')
ORDER BY `row_type` DESC, `Series Ep.`, `Episode`;

nl: 訪問された国には"USA"または"オーストラリア"が含まれているエピソードの場合,それぞれのプレゼンターの プレゼンター名,Total_Episodes (プレゼンターごとにそれらのエピソードの数),およびUSA (訪問された国には"USA"と別には0が含まれている場合,SUMは1で数え),少なくとも1つのそのようなエピソードを持つプレゼンターのみを表示し,outputをTotal_Episodesによって下回順に並べます.
sql:
SELECT `Presenter` AS `Presenter`, COUNT(*) AS `Total_Episodes`,
SUM(CASE WHEN `Countries Visited` LIKE '%USA%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) `USA`
FROM `table_m_1764886255760_64798c0d_15211468_1`
WHERE `Countries Visited` LIKE '%USA%' OR `Countries Visited` LIKE '%Australia%'
GROUP BY `Presenter`
HAVING COUNT(*)>0
ORDER BY `Total_Episodes` DESC;
db_sql:
SELECT col3 AS col3, COUNT(*) AS `Total_Episodes`,
SUM(CASE WHEN col5 LIKE '%USA%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) `USA`

WHERE col5 LIKE '%USA%' OR col5 LIKE '%Australia%'
GROUP BY col3
HAVING COUNT(*)>0

nl: ベルゲン,マック,バルチラエンジンを搭載した3万3千5千フィート,4,000トン未満の候補船を教えてください 7,000HP以上 名前,長さ,トンネージ,製造年,建造者,エンジンの名前,古い名前,最初に列挙してください.
sql:
SELECT
  `ship_name`,
  CAST(REPLACE(`Length`, ' Feet', '') AS REAL) AS `length_ft`,
  `Length`,
  `Tonnage`,
  `Year`,
  `builder`,
  `Engines`,
  `Horsepowers`,
  `former_names_list`,
  CASE
    WHEN `Engines` LIKE '%Bergen Diesel%' THEN '`Bergen Diesel`'
    WHEN `Engines` LIKE '%MAK%' THEN '`MAK`'
    WHEN `Engines` LIKE '%Wärtsilä%' THEN '`Wärtsilä`'
    ELSE '`Other`'
  END AS `Engine_Make_Tag`,
  '`' || `ship_name` || '`' AS `ShipName_backticked`,
  '`' || `former_names_list` || '`' AS `Former_Names_backticked`
FROM `table_m_1764886261451_73311718_15230458_1`
WHERE CAST(REPLACE(`Length`, ' Feet', '') AS REAL) BETWEEN 300 AND 350
  AND `Tonnage` < 4000
  AND (`Engines` LIKE '%Bergen Diesel%' OR `Engines` LIKE '%MAK%' OR `Engines` LIKE '%Wärtsilä%')
  AND `Horsepowers` >= 7000
ORDER BY `Year` ASC, `Horsepowers` DESC;
db_sql:
SELECT
  col0,
  CAST(REPLACE(col1, ' Feet', '') AS REAL) AS `length_ft`,
  col1,
  col2,
  col4,
  col3,
  col5,
  col6,
  col7,
  CASE
    WHEN col5 LIKE '%Bergen Diesel%' THEN '`Bergen Diesel`'
    WHEN col5 LIKE '%MAK%' THEN '`MAK`'
    WHEN col5 LIKE '%Wärtsilä%' THEN '`Wärtsilä`'
    ELSE '`Other`'
  END AS `Engine_Make_Tag`,
  '`' || col0 || '`' AS `ShipName_backticked`,
  '`' || col7 || '`' AS `Former_Names_backticked`
FROM `table_m_1764886261451_73311718_15230458_1`
WHERE CAST(REPLACE(col1, ' Feet', '') AS REAL) BETWEEN 300 AND 350
  AND col2 < 4000
  AND (col5 LIKE '%Bergen Diesel%' OR col5 LIKE '%MAK%' OR col5 LIKE '%Wärtsilä%')
  AND col6 >= 7000
ORDER BY col4 ASC, col6 DESC;

nl: 各異なる国に対して,Wins数,AVG Winner Share Pct は ROUND(AVG(CAST(Winners share ($) AS REAL) /Purse ($) 6) と定義され,そのAVGが6位数に丸められるときに"Below AVG payout"と書かれた決済フラッグは <0.142 であるため,0位以上の勝利を有する国のみを返却し,出力を100列に制限する.
sql: SELECT DISTINCT `Country`, COUNT(*) `Wins`, ROUND(AVG(CAST(`Winner share percentage of purse` AS REAL)/`Winner share percentage of purse`),6) `Avg Winner Share Pct`, CASE WHEN ROUND(AVG(CAST(`Winner share percentage of purse` AS REAL)/`Winner share percentage of purse`),6) < 0.142 THEN '`Below avg payout`' END `Payout flag` FROM `table_m_1764886309675_6e2a60e2_15315816_1` GROUP BY `Country` HAVING COUNT(*)>0 LIMIT 100;
db_sql: SELECT DISTINCT col3, COUNT(*) `Wins`, ROUND(AVG(CAST(col6 AS REAL)/col6),6) `Avg Winner Share Pct`, CASE WHEN ROUND(AVG(CAST(col6 AS REAL)/col6),6) < 0.142 THEN '`Below avg payout`' END `Payout flag` FROM `table_m_1764886309675_6e2a60e2_15315816_1` GROUP BY col3 HAVING COUNT(*)>0 LIMIT 100;
db_result: [('Australia', 2, 1.0, None), ('Brazil', 1, 1.0, None), ('Canada', 1, 1.0, None), ('Paraguay', 1, 1.0, None), ('South Korea', 3, 1.0, None), ('Taiwan', 1, 1.0, None), ('Thailand', 1, 1.0, None), ('United States', 3, 1.0, None)]

nl: プレー = 20 のエントリー,およびSUM ((ポイント) >= 10 のグループによるチームによるグループ結果については,チーム,ポイント,ゴール差は (For - Against) と計算され"Palmeiras"とラベル付けされ,ポイントごとにポイント (Point / Played) が5行に制限され,ポイントによって順序付けられ,何ですか?
sql:

FROM `table_m_1764886317480_43d6e027_15318779_1`
WHERE `Played` = 20
GROUP BY `team_name`
HAVING SUM(`Points`) >= 10

db_sql:

FROM `table_m_1764886317480_43d6e027_15318779_1`
WHERE col3 = 20
GROUP BY col1
HAVING SUM(col2) >= 10
ORDER BY col2

nl: 各監督 (ディレクター) のエピソード数 (タイトルエントリー数),AVG視聴者 (米国視聴者のAVG (百万)),MAX視聴者 (米国視聴者のMAX (百万)),およびMIN視聴者 (米国視聴者のMIN (百万) をリストする.
sql:
SELECT t1.`Directed by`, COUNT(t1.`Title`) `Episode Count`, AVG(t1.`U.S. viewers (million)`) `Avg Viewers`, MAX(t1.`U.S. viewers (million)`) `Max Viewers`, MIN(t1.`U.S. viewers (million)`) `Min Viewers`
FROM `table_m_1764886448184_9b828c94_15584067_7` t1 JOIN `table_m_1764886448184_9b828c94_15584067_7` t2 ON t2.`Directed by` = t1.`Directed by`
WHERE t1.`U.S. viewers (million)` >= t2.`U.S. viewers (million)`

db_sql:

nl: クラブの5つのクラブ (制限 5) をリストし,ファーストシーズン > 0,各クラブに スーペルエッタン (スーペルエッタン) のシーズン数,秒レベル (セカンドティアー) のシーズン数,Is_Husqvarna フィールドが true に等しいときのクラブ = 'Husqvarna FF', NearestGap がそのクラブのファーストシーズンと他のクラブのファーストシーズン間の絶対差に等しいときの Is_Husqvarna フィールドをリストし,Penetration が"High penetration"でなければならない Penetration が (スーペルエッタン * 1.0 / (秒レベル + 0 のシーズン数) > 0.5ッ (Low penetration), Penetration が命令され,Penetration が NearestGap に下降する?
sql:
SELECT
  m.`Club` `Club`,
  m.`Number of seasons in Superettan` `Superettan`,
  m.`Number of seasons in second tier` `SecondTier`,
  (m.`Club` = '`Husqvarna FF`') `Is_Husqvarna`,
  ABS(m.`First season` - j.`First season`) `NearestGap`,
  CASE WHEN (m.`Number of seasons in Superettan` * 1.0 / (m.`Number of seasons in second tier` + 0)) > 0.5 THEN '`High penetration`' ELSE '`Low penetration`' END AS `Penetration`
FROM `table_m_1764886468425_3f4eb0d8_1560673_1` m
JOIN `table_m_1764886468425_3f4eb0d8_1560673_1` j ON j.`Club` != m.`Club`
WHERE m.`First season` > 0
GROUP BY m.`Club`
ORDER BY `Penetration` DESC, `NearestGap`
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT
  m.col0 col0,
  m.col4 `Superettan`,
  m.col5 `SecondTier`,
  (m.col0 = '`Husqvarna FF`') `Is_Husqvarna`,
  ABS(m.col2 - j.col2) `NearestGap`,
  CASE WHEN (m.col4 * 1.0 / (m.col5 + 0)) > 0.5 THEN '`High penetration`' ELSE '`Low penetration`' END AS `Penetration`
FROM `table_m_1764886468425_3f4eb0d8_1560673_1` m
JOIN `table_m_1764886468425_3f4eb0d8_1560673_1` j ON j.col0 != m.col0
WHERE m.col2 > 0
GROUP BY m.col0
ORDER BY `Penetration` DESC, `NearestGap`
LIMIT 5;

    `High assists`,

    CAST(REPLACE(SUBSTR(`Location Attendance`, INSTR(`Location Attendance`, 'Centre') + LENGTH('Centre') + 1), ',', '') AS INTEGER) AS `AttendanceNumeric`,
    CASE WHEN `final_score` LIKE '%(OT)%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS `is_ot`,
    CASE WHEN CAST(REPLACE(SUBSTR(`Location Attendance`, INSTR(`Location Attendance`, 'Centre') + LENGTH('Centre') + 1), ',', '') AS INTEGER) > 19000 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS `HighAttendance`
  FROM `table_m_1764886653532_e9f6c60d_15869204_6`
  WHERE `Location Attendance` LIKE '%Air Canada Centre%'
)

  `game_id`,

  `Team`,

  `is_ot`,

  COUNT(*) OVER (PARTITION BY `is_ot`) AS `CountByOTFlag`,

FROM `home_games`
ORDER BY `is_ot` DESC, `AttendanceNumeric` DESC, `game_id` ASC;

nl: ゲーム > 45 の記録に限定された各チーム (チームによってグループ) に対して,ゲーム (COUNT(*) の合計はどれですか? W で始まるスコアの合計として勝利, L で始まるスコアの合計として損失, 位置 attendance の最後の6文字から kommaを削除することによって得られた数値の最大値として Max Attendance, そして Avg Attendance がその数値の丸化平均として,次に W の順序で順序付けされたトップ10 のチームをリストしてください.
sql:
SELECT `Team`,
       COUNT(*) `Games`,
       SUM(substr(`Outcome_and_Venue_Attendance`,1,1)='W') `Wins`,
       SUM(substr(`Outcome_and_Venue_Attendance`,1,1)='L') `Losses`,
       MAX(replace(substr(`Outcome_and_Venue_Attendance`,-6),',','')+0) `Max Attendance`,
       ROUND(AVG(replace(substr(`Outcome_and_Venue_Attendance`,-6),',','')+0)) `Avg Attendance`
FROM `table_m_1764886666121_3cce0583_15869204_7`
WHERE `Game` > 45
GROUP BY `Team`
ORDER BY `Wins` DESC
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT col2,
       COUNT(*) `Games`,
       SUM(substr(col7,1,1)='W') `Wins`,
       SUM(substr(col7,1,1)='L') `Losses`,
       MAX(replace(substr(col7,-6),',','')+0) `Max Attendance`,
       ROUND(AVG(replace(substr(col7,-6),',','')+0)) `Avg Attendance`
FROM `table_m_1764886666121_3cce0583_15869204_7`
WHERE col0 > 45
GROUP BY col2
ORDER BY `Wins` DESC
LIMIT 10;

nl: t.Seasons > s.Seasons AND s.Seasons >= 1 で表を自分自身に結合し,同時に"Project Runway Canada"と"Project Runway Malaysia"という空文字列の2つの列を返し, 国によってグループ化して,その COUNT t.Seasons) > 0 のグループだけを保持し,結果を10列に制限することで生成される"Seasons Above Peers"の"COUNT t.Seasons) はどれですか?
sql:
SELECT DISTINCT t.`Country`, COUNT(t.`Seasons`) `Seasons Above Peers`, '' `Project Runway Canada`, '' `Project Runway Malaysia`
FROM `table_m_1764886770466_a47aa671_1597866_3` t
JOIN `table_m_1764886770466_a47aa671_1597866_3` s
ON t.`Seasons` > s.`Seasons` AND s.`Seasons` >= 1
WHERE t.`Seasons` > 1
GROUP BY t.`Country`
HAVING COUNT(t.`Seasons`) > 0
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT t.col0, COUNT(t.col5) `Seasons Above Peers`, '' `Project Runway Canada`, '' `Project Runway Malaysia`
FROM `table_m_1764886770466_a47aa671_1597866_3` t
JOIN `table_m_1764886770466_a47aa671_1597866_3` s
ON t.col5 > s.col5 AND s.col5 >= 1
WHERE t.col5 > 1
GROUP BY t.col0
HAVING COUNT(t.col5) > 0
LIMIT 10;

WITH `table_m_1764886920749_340b2ff6_16227492_1`(`#`,`Date`,`Home/Away Opponent`,`Home/Away Opponent`,`Score`,`Attendance`,`Record`) AS (

nl: プロヴィンス,国連地域,人口,面積 (km2),プロヴィンスの密度 ((人口*1.0) /地域 (km2)),および地域の avg_density (AVG(人口*1.0) /地域 (km2) を示す各州は,国連地域によって地域 (km2) >0と (人口*1.0) /地域 (km2) >= avg_densityを指定し,20列に制限されている地域 (km2) を含む地域 (州) と地域 (州) に結合した結果である.
sql:
WITH `regional_stats` AS (
  SELECT `U.N. Region`, AVG((`Population`*1.0)/`Area (km²)`) `avg_density`, SUM(`Population`) `total_pop`
  FROM `table_m_1764886949931_40e92049_16278349_1`
  GROUP BY `U.N. Region`
)
SELECT DISTINCT t.`Province`, t.`U.N. Region`, t.`Population`, t.`Area (km²)`, (t.`Population`*1.0)/t.`Area (km²)` `density`, rs.`avg_density`
FROM `table_m_1764886949931_40e92049_16278349_1` t NATURAL JOIN `regional_stats` rs
WHERE t.`Area (km²)` > 0 AND (t.`Population`*1.0)/t.`Area (km²)` >= rs.`avg_density`
ORDER BY `U.N. Region`
LIMIT 20;
db_sql:
WITH `regional_stats` AS (
  SELECT col7, AVG((col4*1.0)/col5) `avg_density`, SUM(col4) `total_pop`
  FROM `table_m_1764886949931_40e92049_16278349_1`
  GROUP BY col7
)
SELECT DISTINCT t.col0, t.col7, t.col4, t.col5, (t.col4*1.0)/t.col5 `density`, rs.`avg_density`
FROM `table_m_1764886949931_40e92049_16278349_1` t NATURAL JOIN `regional_stats` rs
WHERE t.col5 > 0 AND (t.col4*1.0)/t.col5 >= rs.`avg_density`
ORDER BY col7
LIMIT 20;

nl: どちらのチームが ACCの勝利比率よりも 勝利比率を高く,ホームで強かったのか?
sql:
SELECT DISTINCT `Team`,
 (CAST(SUBSTR(`All Games`, 1, INSTR(`All Games`, '–')-1) AS REAL) / (CAST(SUBSTR(`All Games`, 1, INSTR(`All Games`, '–')-1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTR(`All Games`, INSTR(`All Games`, '–')+1) AS REAL))) AS `All_Games_Pct`,
 CAST(`ACC %` AS REAL) AS `ACC_Pct`,
 CASE WHEN (
   (CAST(SUBSTR(`All Home`, 1, INSTR(`All Home`, '–')-1) AS REAL) / (CAST(SUBSTR(`All Home`, 1, INSTR(`All Home`, '–')-1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTR(`All Home`, INSTR(`All Home`, '–')+1) AS REAL)))
   >
   (CAST(SUBSTR(`All Road`, 1, INSTR(`All Road`, '–')-1) AS REAL) / (CAST(SUBSTR(`All Road`, 1, INSTR(`All Road`, '–')-1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTR(`All Road`, INSTR(`All Road`, '–')+1) AS REAL)))
 ) THEN 'Stronger at Home' END AS `Home_Strength`
FROM `table_m_1764887035803_020cf9c8_16372244_1`
WHERE (CAST(SUBSTR(`All Games`, 1, INSTR(`All Games`, '–')-1) AS REAL) / (CAST(SUBSTR(`All Games`, 1, INSTR(`All Games`, '–')-1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTR(`All Games`, INSTR(`All Games`, '–')+1) AS REAL))) > CAST(`ACC %` AS REAL)
LIMIT 8;
db_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT col0,
 (CAST(SUBSTR(col5, 1, INSTR(col5, '–')-1) AS REAL) / (CAST(SUBSTR(col5, 1, INSTR(col5, '–')-1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTR(col5, INSTR(col5, '–')+1) AS REAL))) AS `All_Games_Pct`,
 CAST(col2 AS REAL) AS `ACC_Pct`,
 CASE WHEN (
   (CAST(SUBSTR(col6, 1, INSTR(col6, '–')-1) AS REAL) / (CAST(SUBSTR(col6, 1, INSTR(col6, '–')-1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTR(col6, INSTR(col6, '–')+1) AS REAL)))
   >
   (CAST(SUBSTR(col7, 1, INSTR(col7, '–')-1) AS REAL) / (CAST(SUBSTR(col7, 1, INSTR(col7, '–')-1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTR(col7, INSTR(col7, '–')+1) AS REAL)))
 ) THEN 'Stronger at Home' END AS `Home_Strength`
FROM `table_m_1764887035803_020cf9c8_16372244_1`
WHERE (CAST(SUBSTR(col5, 1, INSTR(col5, '–')-1) AS REAL) / (CAST(SUBSTR(col5, 1, INSTR(col5, '–')-1) AS REAL) + CAST(SUBSTR(col5, INSTR(col5, '–')+1) AS REAL))) > CAST(col2 AS REAL)
LIMIT 8;

nl: 最低3話を監督した監督 ("ディレクターによる") をリストし,それぞれにディレクター (ディレクター),監督されたエピソードの数 (エピソード),異なる"脚本による"名前 (ライター) の逗号別列をリストし,制作 符号範囲を MAX("制作 符号") - MIN("制作 符号") (コードラング) として計算する.
sql:
WITH `directors` AS (
 SELECT `Directed by`, COUNT(*) `EpisodeCount`
 FROM `table_m_1764887069505_2eccd213_16384596_4`
 GROUP BY `Directed by`
 HAVING `EpisodeCount` >= 3
)
SELECT `directors`.`Directed by` `Director`, `EpisodeCount` `Episodes`, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT `Written by`) `Writers`, MAX(`Production Code`) - MIN(`Production Code`) `CodeRange`
FROM `directors`
JOIN `table_m_1764887069505_2eccd213_16384596_4` USING (`Directed by`)
GROUP BY `directors`.`Directed by`
ORDER BY `Episodes` DESC
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
WITH `directors` AS (
 SELECT col2, COUNT(*) `EpisodeCount`
 FROM `table_m_1764887069505_2eccd213_16384596_4`
 GROUP BY col2
 HAVING `EpisodeCount` >= 3
)
SELECT `directors`.col2 `Director`, `EpisodeCount` `Episodes`, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT col3) `Writers`, MAX(col5) - MIN(col5) `CodeRange`
FROM `directors`
JOIN `table_m_1764887069505_2eccd213_16384596_4` USING (col2)
GROUP BY `directors`.col2
ORDER BY `Episodes` DESC
LIMIT 10;

nl: 各 Ground に対して, Crowd > 10000 のゲームのみを考慮し,Count の Grounds を含めてのみ,Count の Grounds は,Count の Ground,COUNT (COUNT(*) は,Avg の群れとして丸められた平均群れ (ROUND(AVG(Crowd))) は,最大幅 (家庭チームのスコアにおける括弧内数値とAway チームのスコア内括弧内数値の絶対差のMAX) は,Max幅として,Close のゲーム数 (その絶対差が <= 5) は,Avg の群れが上昇する順序で決まります.
sql:
SELECT
`Ground`,
COUNT(*) `Matches`,
ROUND(AVG(`Crowd`)) `Avg crowd`,
MAX(abs(
 (substr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, '(')+1, instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, ')') - instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, '(') -1)+0)
 -
 (substr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, '(')+1, instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, ')') - instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, '(') -1)+0)
)) `Max margin`,
SUM((abs(
 (substr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, '(')+1, instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, ')') - instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, '(') -1)+0)
 -
 (substr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, '(')+1, instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, ')') - instr(`Match score (Home vs Away)`, '(') -1)+0)
) <= 5)) `Close games`
FROM `table_m_1764887079815_3cd58b64_16387953_1`
WHERE `Crowd` > 10000
GROUP BY `Ground`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Avg crowd` ASC;
db_sql:
SELECT
col2,
COUNT(*) `Matches`,
ROUND(AVG(col3)) `Avg crowd`,
MAX(abs(
 (substr(col6, instr(col6, '(')+1, instr(col6, ')') - instr(col6, '(') -1)+0)
 -
 (substr(col6, instr(col6, '(')+1, instr(col6, ')') - instr(col6, '(') -1)+0)
)) `Max margin`,
SUM((abs(
 (substr(col6, instr(col6, '(')+1, instr(col6, ')') - instr(col6, '(') -1)+0)
 -
 (substr(col6, instr(col6, '(')+1, instr(col6, ')') - instr(col6, '(') -1)+0)
) <= 5)) `Close games`
FROM `table_m_1764887079815_3cd58b64_16387953_1`
WHERE col3 > 10000
GROUP BY col2
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Avg crowd` ASC;

nl: グラウンド,そのグラウンド (COUNT(*) の試合数,家庭チームスコアと アウェーチームスコア (AVG(ABS(家庭チームスコアから括弧合計 - アウェーチームスコアから括弧合計))),平均集団 (AVG(集団) とそれらの括弧合計の最大絶対差 (MAX(ABS(...))) の間の絶対差の平均を挙げてください.
sql:
SELECT `Ground`, COUNT(*), AVG(ABS(
  (SUBSTR(`Home team score`, INSTR(`Home team score`, '(')+1, INSTR(`Home team score`, ')') - INSTR(`Home team score`, '(') - 1) + 0)
  -
  (SUBSTR(`Away team score`, INSTR(`Away team score`, '(')+1, INSTR(`Away team score`, ')') - INSTR(`Away team score`, '(') - 1) + 0)
)), AVG(`Crowd`), MAX(ABS(
  (SUBSTR(`Home team score`, INSTR(`Home team score`, '(')+1, INSTR(`Home team score`, ')') - INSTR(`Home team score`, '(') - 1) + 0)
  -
  (SUBSTR(`Away team score`, INSTR(`Away team score`, '(')+1, INSTR(`Away team score`, ')') - INSTR(`Away team score`, '(') - 1) + 0)
))
FROM `table_m_1764887108419_cd627d8a_16388506_1`
GROUP BY `Ground`
HAVING AVG(`Crowd`) > 8000
ORDER BY 3
LIMIT 3;
db_sql:
SELECT col4, COUNT(*), AVG(ABS(
  (SUBSTR(col1, INSTR(col1, '(')+1, INSTR(col1, ')') - INSTR(col1, '(') - 1) + 0)
  -
  (SUBSTR(col3, INSTR(col3, '(')+1, INSTR(col3, ')') - INSTR(col3, '(') - 1) + 0)
)), AVG(col5), MAX(ABS(
  (SUBSTR(col1, INSTR(col1, '(')+1, INSTR(col1, ')') - INSTR(col1, '(') - 1) + 0)
  -
  (SUBSTR(col3, INSTR(col3, '(')+1, INSTR(col3, ')') - INSTR(col3, '(') - 1) + 0)
))
FROM `table_m_1764887108419_cd627d8a_16388506_1`
GROUP BY col4
HAVING AVG(col5) > 8000
ORDER BY 3
LIMIT 3;

nl: Week, デイト,Opponent,Game site,および 出席を指定し,最終スコアのサブストリングとしてチームポイントを計算します. キャラクター3から""直前に",Opponent points as the substring after "",Margin as (Opponent points - Team points),Opponent strings does not contain 'at' and 0 otherwise, and 出席 per margin equal to 出席 divided by (Margin + 1), 出席=10000と計算された Margin=10の行のみを含む.
sql:
SELECT
`Week`,
`Date`,
`Opponent`,
`Game site`,
`Attendance`,
((substr(`Final score`, instr(`Final score`, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(`Final score`, 3, instr(`Final score`, '–') - 3) * 1)) `Margin`,
((substr(`Final score`, 3, instr(`Final score`, '–') - 3) * 1)) `Team points`,
((substr(`Final score`, instr(`Final score`, '–')+1) * 1)) `Opponent points`,
((instr(`Opponent`, 'at ') = 0) * 1) `Home flag`,
(`Attendance` / (((substr(`Final score`, instr(`Final score`, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(`Final score`, 3, instr(`Final score`, '–') - 3) * 1) + 1))) `Attendance per margin`
FROM `table_m_1764887133810_cca7f843_1639689_2`
WHERE `Attendance` >= 10000 AND (((substr(`Final score`, instr(`Final score`, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(`Final score`, 3, instr(`Final score`, '–') - 3) * 1)) >= 10);
db_sql:
SELECT
col0,
col1,
col3,
col6,
col7,
((substr(col4, instr(col4, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(col4, 3, instr(col4, '–') - 3) * 1)) `Margin`,
((substr(col4, 3, instr(col4, '–') - 3) * 1)) `Team points`,
((substr(col4, instr(col4, '–')+1) * 1)) `Opponent points`,
((instr(col3, 'at ') = 0) * 1) `Home flag`,
(col7 / (((substr(col4, instr(col4, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(col4, 3, instr(col4, '–') - 3) * 1) + 1))) `Attendance per margin`
FROM `table_m_1764887133810_cca7f843_1639689_2`
WHERE col7 >= 10000 AND (((substr(col4, instr(col4, '–')+1) * 1) - (substr(col4, 3, instr(col4, '–') - 3) * 1)) >= 10);

nl: 同じホームリンクを共有し,機関 A <機関 B を満たしている機関 (機関 A と機関 B) のペアを提供し,機関 A,機関 B,ホームリンクを表示し,A の登録がB の登録よりも大きいかどうかによって"A より大きい" /"B より大きい" /"等しい"と記された登録比較を提供し,A の登録がB の登録よりも大きいか/少なくか/等しいかによって,およびA (会議 A) とB (会議 B) のプライマリー会議を表示し,ホームリンクによって注文され,最初に"A より大きい"と登録比較によって上昇し,結果100に制限されます.

5 までの結果については,文字通り"レキシントン",学年,Lexington_Appearances"を総数として計算する. 1=1 OR 0=1 THEN ((Volleyball LIKE '%レキシントン%') + ( Cross Country LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Football LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Tennis LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Golf LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Basketball LIKE '%レキシントン%) + (Swimming LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Softball LIKE '%レキシントン%') + (Track & フィールド LIKE '% Lex Lex Lexiントン%'D) 各学年 (Volleyball LIKE '%レキシントン%') に関する各学年 (Volleyball LIKE '%レキシントン%') に関する各学
sql: SELECT '`Lexington`', `academic_year`, SUM(CASE WHEN 1=1 OR 0=1 THEN ((`volleyball_team` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`cross_country_team` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Soccer` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Tennis` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Golf` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Basketball` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Swimming` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Softball` LIKE '%Lexington%') + (`Track & Field` LIKE '%Lexington%')) END) AS `Lexington_Appearances` FROM `table_m_1764887163542_08636f34_16423070_4` WHERE ((`volleyball_team` || `cross_country_team` || `Soccer` || `Tennis` || `Golf` || `Basketball` || `Swimming` || `Softball` || `Track & Field`) LIKE '%Lexington%') AND 1=1 GROUP BY `academic_year` HAVING `Lexington_Appearances` > 0 ORDER BY `Lexington_Appearances` LIMIT 5;
db_sql: SELECT '`Lexington`', col0, SUM(CASE WHEN 1=1 OR 0=1 THEN ((col1 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col2 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col3 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col4 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col5 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col6 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col7 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col8 LIKE '%Lexington%') + (col9 LIKE '%Lexington%')) END) AS `Lexington_Appearances` FROM `table_m_1764887163542_08636f34_16423070_4` WHERE ((col1 || col2 || col3 || col4 || col5 || col6 || col7 || col8 || col9) LIKE '%Lexington%') AND 1=1 GROUP BY col0 HAVING `Lexington_Appearances` > 0 ORDER BY `Lexington_Appearances` LIMIT 5;

nl: `Directed by ` (COUNT(*) の値は,シーズンで `No. との列の中で1以上のエピソード (HAVING COUNT(*) > 1) を含む.そして,それぞれに `Directed by `返信する `Directed by `名, `Episodes directed ` (COUNT(*) とのエピソード数, MIN(`Original air date`) を `First air date`,そして MAX(`Original air date`) を `Last air date`, output を `Episodes directed `下回順序で?
sql:
SELECT `Directed by`, COUNT(*) `Episodes directed`, MIN(`Original air date`) `First air date`, MAX(`Original air date`) `Last air date`
FROM `table_m_1764887181992_dcc69b6b_16432167_1`
WHERE `No. in season`>0
GROUP BY `Directed by`
HAVING COUNT(*)>1
ORDER BY `Episodes directed` DESC;
db_sql:
SELECT col3, COUNT(*) `Episodes directed`, MIN(col4) `First air date`, MAX(col4) `Last air date`
FROM `table_m_1764887181992_dcc69b6b_16432167_1`
WHERE col1>0
GROUP BY col3
HAVING COUNT(*)>1
ORDER BY `Episodes directed` DESC;

nl: 銃は m/v ft/s と マックス.高度 (ft) の両方で打っている.それぞれの銃を Better_than_peers (他の銃のカウント) に, Avg_Delta_v (この銃の m/v ft/s を引いて他の銃を引いて) に, Avg_Delta_25 (この銃の Time to ft (m) を 25° (秒) を引いて他の銃を引いて) に, Avg_Delta_h (この銃の マックス.高度 (ft) を引いて) に, Avg_Delta_v (下降) にのみトップ5の銃を返す.
sql:
SELECT t.`weapon`, COUNT(*) AS `Better_than_peers`, AVG(t.`velocity_ft_per_second` - t2.`velocity_ft_per_second`) `Avg_Delta_v`, AVG((t.`time_to_25_degrees_meters_seconds`+0.0) - (t2.`time_to_25_degrees_meters_seconds`+0.0)) `Avg_Delta_25`, AVG(t.`Max. height (ft)` - t2.`Max. height (ft)`) `Avg_Delta_h`
FROM `table_m_1764887188394_a4359ef7_16439764_1` t
INNER JOIN `table_m_1764887188394_a4359ef7_16439764_1` t2 ON t.`weapon` <> t2.`weapon`
WHERE (t.`velocity_ft_per_second` > t2.`velocity_ft_per_second`) AND (t.`Max. height (ft)` > t2.`Max. height (ft)`)
GROUP BY t.`weapon`
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Avg_Delta_v` DESC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT t.col0, COUNT(*) AS `Better_than_peers`, AVG(t.col1 - t2.col1) `Avg_Delta_v`, AVG((t.col3+0.0) - (t2.col3+0.0)) `Avg_Delta_25`, AVG(t.col6 - t2.col6) `Avg_Delta_h`
FROM `table_m_1764887188394_a4359ef7_16439764_1` t
INNER JOIN `table_m_1764887188394_a4359ef7_16439764_1` t2 ON t.col0 <> t2.col0
WHERE (t.col1 > t2.col1) AND (t.col6 > t2.col6)
GROUP BY t.col0
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY `Avg_Delta_v` DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: 各チーム (ローカルとスキップ) をW >=6でリストし,W,L,PF,PA,ポイント差=PF - PA,ゲームごとに差= (PF - PA) /(W + L) を2桁に丸め,エンドネット=エンド・ウィン -エンド・ウィン,ショット比率=ショット %を01比率に丸め,3桁に丸め,ストールシェア=ストールエンド/ (エンド・ウィン +エンド・ウィン) を3桁に丸め.

nl: 長さ (m) > 0 の列のみを考慮すると,ペーブメントの各タイプに対して,合計_長さ = SUM (長さ (m)), avg_climb = AVG (%)),およびカウント = COUNT (COUNT) を計算すると,難度_スコア = (総_長さ * avg_climb / 100.0) を計算する. DESC (type, total_length, avg_climb, count, and difficulty_score) を注文したときにどちらのペーブメントタイプが最大の難度_スコアを持っているのか?
sql:
WITH `pavements` AS (
  SELECT `Pavement` AS `type`, SUM(`length_in_meters`) AS `total_length`, AVG(`average_climb_percentage`) AS `avg_climb`, COUNT(*) AS `count`
  FROM `table_m_1764887316951_21d890cd_16654785_2`
  WHERE `length_in_meters` > 0
  GROUP BY `Pavement`
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
)
SELECT `type`, `total_length`, `avg_climb`, `count`, (`total_length` * `avg_climb` / 100.0) AS `difficulty_score`
FROM `pavements`
ORDER BY `difficulty_score` DESC
LIMIT 2;
db_sql:
WITH `pavements` AS (
  SELECT col3 AS `type`, SUM(col4) AS `total_length`, AVG(col5) AS `avg_climb`, COUNT(*) AS `count`
  FROM `table_m_1764887316951_21d890cd_16654785_2`
  WHERE col4 > 0
  GROUP BY col3
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
)
SELECT `type`, `total_length`, `avg_climb`, `count`, (`total_length` * `avg_climb` / 100.0) AS `difficulty_score`
FROM `pavements`
ORDER BY `difficulty_score` DESC
LIMIT 2;

nl: [Na + ](mmol/L) > 0 と [Glucose](mmol/L) >= 0 のエントリについては, (2 * [Na + ](mmol/L) + [Glucose](mmol/L)) <= 295 と "Non-アイソトニック"でない場合は",アイソトニック"と分類する.
sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN (2*`[Na + ](mmol/L)` + `[Glucose](mmol/L)`) <= 295 THEN 'Isotonic' ELSE 'Non-Isotonic' END AS `Classification`, COUNT(*) `D5W`, AVG(`[Na + ](mmol/L)`)
FROM `table_m_1764887334170_6cff174f_16689223_1`
WHERE (`[Na + ](mmol/L)` > 0 AND `[Glucose](mmol/L)` >= 0)
GROUP BY 1
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
LIMIT 3;
db_sql:
SELECT CASE WHEN (2*col2 + col4) <= 295 THEN 'Isotonic' ELSE 'Non-Isotonic' END AS `Classification`, COUNT(*) `D5W`, AVG(col2)
FROM `table_m_1764887334170_6cff174f_16689223_1`
WHERE (col2 > 0 AND col4 >= 0)
GROUP BY 1
HAVING COUNT(*) > 0
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
LIMIT 3;

nl: チーム (s) により,総スタート (SUM(Starts) を,総勝利 (SUM(Wins) を,勝利割合を (SUM(Wins)*1.0)/SUM(SUM)*100を2桁まで丸め,平均 Avg. 2桁まで丸め,総勝利を"$"と""を剥がした後に丸め,0桁まで丸め (Ken Schrader Racing) と,MIN(Year) とMAXYear を,スタート >0の行のみを使用し,SUM(Starts) >=5を表示したチームのみを返します.
sql:
SELECT `Team(s)`, SUM(`Starts`), SUM(`Wins`), ROUND((SUM(`Wins`)*1.0)/SUM(`Starts`)*100,2), ROUND(AVG(`Avg. Finish` + 0),2), ROUND(SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(`Winnings`,'$',''),',','') + 0),0) AS `Ken Schrader Racing`, MIN(`Year`), MAX(`Year`)
FROM `table_m_1764887374703_9f78ed88_1671401_2`
WHERE `Starts` > 0
GROUP BY `Team(s)`
HAVING SUM(`Starts`) >= 5
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT col9, SUM(col1), SUM(col2), ROUND((SUM(col2)*1.0)/SUM(col1)*100,2), ROUND(AVG(col6 + 0),2), ROUND(SUM(REPLACE(REPLACE(col7,'$',''),',','') + 0),0) AS `Ken Schrader Racing`, MIN(col0), MAX(col0)
FROM `table_m_1764887374703_9f78ed88_1671401_2`
WHERE col1 > 0
GROUP BY col9
HAVING SUM(col1) >= 5
LIMIT 10;

nl: どちらの5つのACCチームが参加者数が10000を超えた試合から,最も高いSUM (参加者数) を得ているか.各ACCチームにとって,COUNT (参加者数) とSUM (参加者数) はどれですか?
sql:
SELECT `ACC Team`, COUNT(`Attendance`), SUM(`Attendance`)
FROM `table_m_1764887389960_2745d16f_1672976_5`
WHERE `Attendance` > 10000
GROUP BY `ACC Team`
ORDER BY SUM(`Attendance`) DESC
LIMIT 5;
db_sql:
SELECT col2, COUNT(col6), SUM(col6)
FROM `table_m_1764887389960_2745d16f_1672976_5`
WHERE col6 > 10000
GROUP BY col2
ORDER BY SUM(col6) DESC
LIMIT 5;

nl: 最大10のソケットグループではソケットを返します. total_modelsを数え,平均TDP (avg_tdp) を返します.ここで avg_tdp は TDP から 'W' のサフィックスを取り除いて数に変換され,平均Mult. (avg_mult) を返します.ここで avg_mult は Mult. から '×' の文字を取り除いて数に変換され,最大 リリース価格 (max_price) と最小 リリース価格 (min_price) は,それぞれの価格が リリース価格 (USD) から '$' を取り除いて計算され,リリース価格 (USD) が '$) を含む場合にのみ考慮されます.
sql:
SELECT DISTINCT `Socket`,
       COUNT(*) "total_models",
       AVG(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '') + 0.0) "avg_tdp",
       AVG(REPLACE(`Mult.`, '×', '') + 0.0) "avg_mult",
       MAX((REPLACE(`Release price ( USD )`, '$', '') + 0.0) * (INSTR(`Release price ( USD )`, '$') > 0)) "max_price",
       MIN((REPLACE(`Release price ( USD )`, '$', '') + 0.0) * (INSTR(`Release price ( USD )`, '$') > 0)) "min_price"
FROM `table_m_1764887407733_376a9e47_16729930_11`
WHERE LENGTH(REPLACE(`TDP`, ' W', '')) > 0 AND LENGTH(REPLACE(`Mult.`, '×', '')) > 0
GROUP BY `Socket`
LIMIT 10;
db_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT col7,
       COUNT(*) "total_models",
       AVG(REPLACE(col6, ' W', '') + 0.0) "avg_tdp",
       AVG(REPLACE(col4, '×', '') + 0.0) "avg_mult",
       MAX((REPLACE(col10, '$', '') + 0.0) * (INSTR(col10, '$') > 0)) "max_price",
       MIN((REPLACE(col10, '$', '') + 0.0) * (INSTR(col10, '$') > 0)) "min_price"
FROM `table_m_1764887407733_376a9e47_16729930_11`
WHERE LENGTH(REPLACE(col6, ' W', '')) > 0 AND LENGTH(REPLACE(col4, '×', '')) > 0
GROUP BY col7
LIMIT 10;
